1234#if QT_CONFIG(animation)
1235/*! \internal */
1236QList<const QObject*> QCommonStylePrivate::animationTargets() const
1237{
1238 return animations.keys();
1239}
1240
1241/*! \internal */
1242QStyleAnimation * QCommonStylePrivate::animation(const QObject *target) const
1243{
1244 return animations.value(key: target);
1245}
1246
1247/*! \internal */
1248void QCommonStylePrivate::startAnimation(QStyleAnimation *animation) const
1249{
1250 Q_Q(const QCommonStyle);
1251 stopAnimation(target: animation->target());
1252 q->connect(asender: animation, SIGNAL(destroyed()), SLOT(_q_removeAnimation()), atype: Qt::UniqueConnection);
1253 animations.insert(key: animation->target(), value: animation);
1254 animation->start();
1255}
1256
1257/*! \internal */
1258void QCommonStylePrivate::stopAnimation(const QObject *target) const
1259{
1260 QStyleAnimation *animation = animations.take(key: target);
1261 if (animation) {
1262 animation->stop();
1263 delete animation;
1264 }
1265}
1266
1267/*! \internal */
1268void QCommonStylePrivate::_q_removeAnimation()
1269{
1270 Q_Q(QCommonStyle);
1271 QObject *animation = q->sender();
1272 if (animation)
1273 animations.remove(key: animation->parent());
1274}
1275#endif
1276
1277/*!
1278 \reimp
1279*/
1280void QCommonStyle::drawControl(ControlElement element, const QStyleOption *opt,
1281 QPainter *p, const QWidget *widget) const
1282{
1283 Q_D(const QCommonStyle);
1284 switch (element) {
1285
1286 case CE_PushButton:
1287 if (const QStyleOptionButton *btn = qstyleoption_cast<const QStyleOptionButton *>(opt)) {
1288 proxy()->drawControl(element: CE_PushButtonBevel, opt: btn, p, w: widget);
1289 QStyleOptionButton subopt = *btn;
1290 subopt.rect = subElementRect(r: SE_PushButtonContents, opt: btn, widget);
1291 proxy()->drawControl(element: CE_PushButtonLabel, opt: &subopt, p, w: widget);
1292 if (btn->state & State_HasFocus) {
1293 QStyleOptionFocusRect fropt;
1294 fropt.QStyleOption::operator=(other: *btn);
1295 fropt.rect = subElementRect(r: SE_PushButtonFocusRect, opt: btn, widget);
1296 proxy()->drawPrimitive(pe: PE_FrameFocusRect, opt: &fropt, p, w: widget);
1297 }
1298 }
1299 break;
1300 case CE_PushButtonBevel:
1301 if (const QStyleOptionButton *btn = qstyleoption_cast<const QStyleOptionButton *>(opt)) {
1302 QRect br = btn->rect;
1303 int dbi = proxy()->pixelMetric(metric: PM_ButtonDefaultIndicator, option: btn, widget);
1304 if (btn->features & QStyleOptionButton::DefaultButton)
1305 proxy()->drawPrimitive(pe: PE_FrameDefaultButton, opt, p, w: widget);
1306 if (btn->features & QStyleOptionButton::AutoDefaultButton)
1307 br.setCoords(xp1: br.left() + dbi, yp1: br.top() + dbi, xp2: br.right() - dbi, yp2: br.bottom() - dbi);
1308 if (!(btn->features & (QStyleOptionButton::Flat | QStyleOptionButton::CommandLinkButton))
1309 || btn->state & (State_Sunken | State_On)
1310 || (btn->features & QStyleOptionButton::CommandLinkButton && btn->state & State_MouseOver)) {
1311 QStyleOptionButton tmpBtn = *btn;
1312 tmpBtn.rect = br;
1313 proxy()->drawPrimitive(pe: PE_PanelButtonCommand, opt: &tmpBtn, p, w: widget);
1314 }
1315 if (btn->features & QStyleOptionButton::HasMenu) {
1316 int mbi = proxy()->pixelMetric(metric: PM_MenuButtonIndicator, option: btn, widget);
1317 QRect ir = btn->rect;
1318 QStyleOptionButton newBtn = *btn;
1319 newBtn.rect = QRect(ir.right() - mbi - 2, ir.height()/2 - mbi/2 + 3, mbi - 6, mbi - 6);
1320 newBtn.rect = visualRect(direction: btn->direction, boundingRect: br, logicalRect: newBtn.rect);
1321 proxy()->drawPrimitive(pe: PE_IndicatorArrowDown, opt: &newBtn, p, w: widget);
1322 }
1323 }
1324 break;
1325 case CE_PushButtonLabel:
1326 if (const QStyleOptionButton *button = qstyleoption_cast<const QStyleOptionButton *>(opt)) {
1327 QRect textRect = button->rect;
1328 int tf = Qt::AlignVCenter | Qt::TextShowMnemonic;
1329 if (!proxy()->styleHint(stylehint: SH_UnderlineShortcut, opt: button, widget))
1330 tf |= Qt::TextHideMnemonic;
1331
1332 if (button->features & QStyleOptionButton::HasMenu) {
1333 int indicatorSize = proxy()->pixelMetric(metric: PM_MenuButtonIndicator, option: button, widget);
1334 if (button->direction == Qt::LeftToRight)
1335 textRect = textRect.adjusted(xp1: 0, yp1: 0, xp2: -indicatorSize, yp2: 0);
1336 else
1337 textRect = textRect.adjusted(xp1: indicatorSize, yp1: 0, xp2: 0, yp2: 0);
1338 }
1339
1340 if (!button->icon.isNull()) {
1341 //Center both icon and text
1342 QIcon::Mode mode = button->state & State_Enabled ? QIcon::Normal : QIcon::Disabled;
1343 if (mode == QIcon::Normal && button->state & State_HasFocus)
1344 mode = QIcon::Active;
1345 QIcon::State state = QIcon::Off;
1346 if (button->state & State_On)
1347 state = QIcon::On;
1348
1349 QPixmap pixmap = button->icon.pixmap(size: button->iconSize, devicePixelRatio: p->device()->devicePixelRatio(), mode, state);
1350 int pixmapWidth = pixmap.width() / pixmap.devicePixelRatio();
1351 int pixmapHeight = pixmap.height() / pixmap.devicePixelRatio();
1352 int labelWidth = pixmapWidth;
1353 int labelHeight = pixmapHeight;
1354 int iconSpacing = 4;//### 4 is currently hardcoded in QPushButton::sizeHint()
1355 if (!button->text.isEmpty()) {
1356 int textWidth = button->fontMetrics.boundingRect(r: opt->rect, flags: tf, text: button->text).width();
1357 labelWidth += (textWidth + iconSpacing);
1358 }
1359
1360 QRect iconRect = QRect(textRect.x() + (textRect.width() - labelWidth) / 2,
1361 textRect.y() + (textRect.height() - labelHeight) / 2,
1362 pixmapWidth, pixmapHeight);
1363
1364 iconRect = visualRect(direction: button->direction, boundingRect: textRect, logicalRect: iconRect);
1365
1366 if (button->direction == Qt::RightToLeft) {
1367 tf |= Qt::AlignRight;
1368 textRect.setRight(iconRect.left() - iconSpacing / 2);
1369 } else {
1370 tf |= Qt::AlignLeft; //left align, we adjust the text-rect instead
1371 textRect.setLeft(iconRect.left() + iconRect.width() + iconSpacing / 2);
1372 }
1373
1374 if (button->state & (State_On | State_Sunken))
1375 iconRect.translate(dx: proxy()->pixelMetric(metric: PM_ButtonShiftHorizontal, option: opt, widget),
1376 dy: proxy()->pixelMetric(metric: PM_ButtonShiftVertical, option: opt, widget));
1377 p->drawPixmap(r: iconRect, pm: pixmap);
1378 } else {
1379 tf |= Qt::AlignHCenter;
1380 }
1381 if (button->state & (State_On | State_Sunken))
1382 textRect.translate(dx: proxy()->pixelMetric(metric: PM_ButtonShiftHorizontal, option: opt, widget),
1383 dy: proxy()->pixelMetric(metric: PM_ButtonShiftVertical, option: opt, widget));
1384
1385 proxy()->drawItemText(painter: p, rect: textRect, flags: tf, pal: button->palette, enabled: (button->state & State_Enabled),
1386 text: button->text, textRole: QPalette::ButtonText);
1387 }
1388 break;
1389 case CE_RadioButton:
1390 case CE_CheckBox:
1391 if (const QStyleOptionButton *btn = qstyleoption_cast<const QStyleOptionButton *>(opt)) {
1392 bool isRadio = (element == CE_RadioButton);
1393 QStyleOptionButton subopt = *btn;
1394 subopt.rect = subElementRect(r: isRadio ? SE_RadioButtonIndicator
1395 : SE_CheckBoxIndicator, opt: btn, widget);
1396 proxy()->drawPrimitive(pe: isRadio ? PE_IndicatorRadioButton : PE_IndicatorCheckBox,
1397 opt: &subopt, p, w: widget);
1398 subopt.rect = subElementRect(r: isRadio ? SE_RadioButtonContents
1399 : SE_CheckBoxContents, opt: btn, widget);
1400 proxy()->drawControl(element: isRadio ? CE_RadioButtonLabel : CE_CheckBoxLabel, opt: &subopt, p, w: widget);
1401 if (btn->state & State_HasFocus) {
1402 QStyleOptionFocusRect fropt;
1403 fropt.QStyleOption::operator=(other: *btn);
1404 fropt.rect = subElementRect(r: isRadio ? SE_RadioButtonFocusRect
1405 : SE_CheckBoxFocusRect, opt: btn, widget);
1406 proxy()->drawPrimitive(pe: PE_FrameFocusRect, opt: &fropt, p, w: widget);
1407 }
1408 }
1409 break;
1410 case CE_RadioButtonLabel:
1411 case CE_CheckBoxLabel:
1412 if (const QStyleOptionButton *btn = qstyleoption_cast<const QStyleOptionButton *>(opt)) {
1413 int alignment = visualAlignment(direction: btn->direction, alignment: Qt::AlignLeft | Qt::AlignVCenter);
1414
1415 if (!proxy()->styleHint(stylehint: SH_UnderlineShortcut, opt: btn, widget))
1416 alignment |= Qt::TextHideMnemonic;
1417 QPixmap pix;
1418 QRect textRect = btn->rect;
1419 if (!btn->icon.isNull()) {
1420 pix = btn->icon.pixmap(size: btn->iconSize, devicePixelRatio: p->device()->devicePixelRatio(), mode: btn->state & State_Enabled ? QIcon::Normal : QIcon::Disabled);
1421 proxy()->drawItemPixmap(painter: p, rect: btn->rect, alignment, pixmap: pix);
1422 if (btn->direction == Qt::RightToLeft)
1423 textRect.setRight(textRect.right() - btn->iconSize.width() - 4);
1424 else
1425 textRect.setLeft(textRect.left() + btn->iconSize.width() + 4);
1426 }
1427 if (!btn->text.isEmpty()){
1428 proxy()->drawItemText(painter: p, rect: textRect, flags: alignment | Qt::TextShowMnemonic,
1429 pal: btn->palette, enabled: btn->state & State_Enabled, text: btn->text, textRole: QPalette::WindowText);
1430 }
1431 }
1432 break;
1433#if QT_CONFIG(menu)
1434 case CE_MenuScroller: {
1435 QStyleOption arrowOpt = *opt;
1436 arrowOpt.state |= State_Enabled;
1437 proxy()->drawPrimitive(pe: ((opt->state & State_DownArrow) ? PE_IndicatorArrowDown : PE_IndicatorArrowUp),
1438 opt: &arrowOpt, p, w: widget);
1439 break; }
1440 case CE_MenuTearoff:
1441 if (opt->state & State_Selected)
1442 p->fillRect(opt->rect, opt->palette.brush(cr: QPalette::Highlight));
1443 else
1444 p->fillRect(opt->rect, opt->palette.brush(cr: QPalette::Button));
1445 p->setPen(QPen(opt->palette.dark().color(), 1, Qt::DashLine));
1446 p->drawLine(x1: opt->rect.x() + 2, y1: opt->rect.y() + opt->rect.height() / 2 - 1,
1447 x2: opt->rect.x() + opt->rect.width() - 4,
1448 y2: opt->rect.y() + opt->rect.height() / 2 - 1);
1449 p->setPen(QPen(opt->palette.light().color(), 1, Qt::DashLine));
1450 p->drawLine(x1: opt->rect.x() + 2, y1: opt->rect.y() + opt->rect.height() / 2,
1451 x2: opt->rect.x() + opt->rect.width() - 4, y2: opt->rect.y() + opt->rect.height() / 2);
1452 break;
1453#endif // QT_CONFIG(menu)
1454#if QT_CONFIG(menubar)
1455 case CE_MenuBarItem:
1456 if (const QStyleOptionMenuItem *mbi = qstyleoption_cast<const QStyleOptionMenuItem *>(opt)) {
1457 int alignment = Qt::AlignCenter | Qt::TextShowMnemonic | Qt::TextDontClip
1458 | Qt::TextSingleLine;
1459 if (!proxy()->styleHint(stylehint: SH_UnderlineShortcut, opt: mbi, widget))
1460 alignment |= Qt::TextHideMnemonic;
1461 int iconExtent = proxy()->pixelMetric(metric: PM_SmallIconSize, option: opt);
1462 QPixmap pix = mbi->icon.pixmap(size: QSize(iconExtent, iconExtent), devicePixelRatio: p->device()->devicePixelRatio(), mode: (mbi->state & State_Enabled) ? QIcon::Normal : QIcon::Disabled);
1463 if (!pix.isNull())
1464 proxy()->drawItemPixmap(painter: p,rect: mbi->rect, alignment, pixmap: pix);
1465 else
1466 proxy()->drawItemText(painter: p, rect: mbi->rect, flags: alignment, pal: mbi->palette, enabled: mbi->state & State_Enabled,
1467 text: mbi->text, textRole: QPalette::ButtonText);
1468 }
1469 break;
1470 case CE_MenuBarEmptyArea:
1471 if (widget && !widget->testAttribute(attribute: Qt::WA_NoSystemBackground))
1472 p->eraseRect(rect: opt->rect);
1473 break;
1474#endif // QT_CONFIG(menubar)
1475#if QT_CONFIG(progressbar)
1476 case CE_ProgressBar:
1477 if (const QStyleOptionProgressBar *pb
1478 = qstyleoption_cast<const QStyleOptionProgressBar *>(opt)) {
1479 QStyleOptionProgressBar subopt = *pb;
1480 subopt.rect = subElementRect(r: SE_ProgressBarGroove, opt: pb, widget);
1481 proxy()->drawControl(element: CE_ProgressBarGroove, opt: &subopt, p, w: widget);
1482 subopt.rect = subElementRect(r: SE_ProgressBarContents, opt: pb, widget);
1483 proxy()->drawControl(element: CE_ProgressBarContents, opt: &subopt, p, w: widget);
1484 if (pb->textVisible) {
1485 subopt.rect = subElementRect(r: SE_ProgressBarLabel, opt: pb, widget);
1486 proxy()->drawControl(element: CE_ProgressBarLabel, opt: &subopt, p, w: widget);
1487 }
1488 }
1489 break;
1490 case CE_ProgressBarGroove:
1491 if (opt->rect.isValid())
1492 qDrawShadePanel(p, r: opt->rect, pal: opt->palette, sunken: true, lineWidth: 1,
1493 fill: &opt->palette.brush(cr: QPalette::Window));
1494 break;
1495 case CE_ProgressBarLabel:
1496 if (const QStyleOptionProgressBar *pb = qstyleoption_cast<const QStyleOptionProgressBar *>(opt)) {
1497 const bool vertical = !(pb->state & QStyle::State_Horizontal);
1498 if (!vertical) {
1499 QPalette::ColorRole textRole = QPalette::NoRole;
1500 if ((pb->textAlignment & Qt::AlignCenter) && pb->textVisible
1501 && ((qint64(pb->progress) - qint64(pb->minimum)) * 2 >= (qint64(pb->maximum) - qint64(pb->minimum)))) {
1502 textRole = QPalette::HighlightedText;
1503 //Draw text shadow, This will increase readability when the background of same color
1504 QRect shadowRect(pb->rect);
1505 shadowRect.translate(dx: 1,dy: 1);
1506 QColor shadowColor = (pb->palette.color(cr: textRole).value() <= 128)
1507 ? QColor(255,255,255,160) : QColor(0,0,0,160);
1508 QPalette shadowPalette = pb->palette;
1509 shadowPalette.setColor(acr: textRole, acolor: shadowColor);
1510 proxy()->drawItemText(painter: p, rect: shadowRect, flags: Qt::AlignCenter | Qt::TextSingleLine, pal: shadowPalette,
1511 enabled: pb->state & State_Enabled, text: pb->text, textRole);
1512 }
1513 proxy()->drawItemText(painter: p, rect: pb->rect, flags: Qt::AlignCenter | Qt::TextSingleLine, pal: pb->palette,
1514 enabled: pb->state & State_Enabled, text: pb->text, textRole);
1515 }
1516 }
1517 break;
1518 case CE_ProgressBarContents:
1519 if (const QStyleOptionProgressBar *pb = qstyleoption_cast<const QStyleOptionProgressBar *>(opt)) {
1520
1521 QRect rect = pb->rect;
1522 const bool vertical = !(pb->state & QStyle::State_Horizontal);
1523 const bool inverted = pb->invertedAppearance;
1524 qint64 minimum = qint64(pb->minimum);
1525 qint64 maximum = qint64(pb->maximum);
1526 qint64 progress = qint64(pb->progress);
1527
1528 QTransform m;
1529
1530 if (vertical) {
1531 rect = QRect(rect.y(), rect.x(), rect.height(), rect.width()); // flip width and height
1532 m.rotate(a: 90);
1533 m.translate(dx: 0, dy: -(rect.height() + rect.y()*2));
1534 }
1535
1536 QPalette pal2 = pb->palette;
1537 // Correct the highlight color if it is the same as the background
1538 if (pal2.highlight() == pal2.window())
1539 pal2.setColor(acr: QPalette::Highlight, acolor: pb->palette.color(cg: QPalette::Active,
1540 cr: QPalette::Highlight));
1541 bool reverse = ((!vertical && (pb->direction == Qt::RightToLeft)) || vertical);
1542 if (inverted)
1543 reverse = !reverse;
1544 int w = rect.width();
1545 if (pb->minimum == 0 && pb->maximum == 0) {
1546 // draw busy indicator
1547 int x = (progress - minimum) % (w * 2);
1548 if (x > w)
1549 x = 2 * w - x;
1550 x = reverse ? rect.right() - x : x + rect.x();
1551 p->setPen(QPen(pal2.highlight().color(), 4));
1552 p->drawLine(x1: x, y1: rect.y(), x2: x, y2: rect.height());
1553 } else {
1554 const int unit_width = proxy()->pixelMetric(metric: PM_ProgressBarChunkWidth, option: pb, widget);
1555 if (!unit_width)
1556 return;
1557
1558 int u;
1559 if (unit_width > 1)
1560 u = ((rect.width() + unit_width) / unit_width);
1561 else
1562 u = w / unit_width;
1563 qint64 p_v = progress - minimum;
1564 qint64 t_s = (maximum - minimum) ? (maximum - minimum) : qint64(1);
1565
1566 if (u > 0 && p_v >= INT_MAX / u && t_s >= u) {
1567 // scale down to something usable.
1568 p_v /= u;
1569 t_s /= u;
1570 }
1571
1572 // nu < tnu, if last chunk is only a partial chunk
1573 int tnu, nu;
1574 tnu = nu = p_v * u / t_s;
1575
1576 if (nu * unit_width > w)
1577 --nu;
1578
1579 // Draw nu units out of a possible u of unit_width
1580 // width, each a rectangle bordered by background
1581 // color, all in a sunken panel with a percentage text
1582 // display at the end.
1583 int x = 0;
1584 int x0 = reverse ? rect.right() - ((unit_width > 1) ? unit_width : 0)
1585 : rect.x();
1586
1587 QStyleOptionProgressBar pbBits = *pb;
1588 pbBits.rect = rect;
1589 pbBits.palette = pal2;
1590 int myY = pbBits.rect.y();
1591 int myHeight = pbBits.rect.height();
1592 pbBits.state = State_None;
1593 for (int i = 0; i < nu; ++i) {
1594 pbBits.rect.setRect(ax: x0 + x, ay: myY, aw: unit_width, ah: myHeight);
1595 pbBits.rect = m.mapRect(QRectF(pbBits.rect)).toRect();
1596 proxy()->drawPrimitive(pe: PE_IndicatorProgressChunk, opt: &pbBits, p, w: widget);
1597 x += reverse ? -unit_width : unit_width;
1598 }
1599
1600 // Draw the last partial chunk to fill up the
1601 // progress bar entirely
1602 if (nu < tnu) {
1603 int pixels_left = w - (nu * unit_width);
1604 int offset = reverse ? x0 + x + unit_width-pixels_left : x0 + x;
1605 pbBits.rect.setRect(ax: offset, ay: myY, aw: pixels_left, ah: myHeight);
1606 pbBits.rect = m.mapRect(QRectF(pbBits.rect)).toRect();
1607 proxy()->drawPrimitive(pe: PE_IndicatorProgressChunk, opt: &pbBits, p, w: widget);
1608 }
1609 }
1610 }
1611 break;
1612#endif // QT_CONFIG(progressbar)
1613 case CE_HeaderLabel:
1614 if (const QStyleOptionHeader *header = qstyleoption_cast<const QStyleOptionHeader *>(opt)) {
1615 QRect rect = header->rect;
1616 if (!header->icon.isNull()) {
1617 int iconExtent = proxy()->pixelMetric(metric: PM_SmallIconSize, option: opt);
1618 QPixmap pixmap
1619 = header->icon.pixmap(size: QSize(iconExtent, iconExtent), devicePixelRatio: p->device()->devicePixelRatio(), mode: (header->state & State_Enabled) ? QIcon::Normal : QIcon::Disabled);
1620 int pixw = pixmap.width() / pixmap.devicePixelRatio();
1621
1622 QRect aligned = alignedRect(direction: header->direction, alignment: QFlag(header->iconAlignment), size: pixmap.size() / pixmap.devicePixelRatio(), rectangle: rect);
1623 QRect inter = aligned.intersected(other: rect);
1624 p->drawPixmap(x: inter.x(), y: inter.y(), pm: pixmap,
1625 sx: inter.x() - aligned.x(), sy: inter.y() - aligned.y(),
1626 sw: aligned.width() * pixmap.devicePixelRatio(),
1627 sh: pixmap.height() * pixmap.devicePixelRatio());
1628
1629 const int margin = proxy()->pixelMetric(metric: QStyle::PM_HeaderMargin, option: opt, widget);
1630 if (header->direction == Qt::LeftToRight)
1631 rect.setLeft(rect.left() + pixw + margin);
1632 else
1633 rect.setRight(rect.right() - pixw - margin);
1634 }
1635 QFontMetrics fm(header->fontMetrics);
1636 if (header->state & QStyle::State_On) {
1637 QFont fnt = p->font();
1638 fnt.setBold(true);
1639 p->setFont(fnt);
1640 fm = QFontMetrics((p->font()));
1641 }
1642 QString text = header->text;
1643 if (const QStyleOptionHeaderV2 *headerV2 = qstyleoption_cast<const QStyleOptionHeaderV2 *>(opt: header)) {
1644 if (headerV2->textElideMode != Qt::ElideNone)
1645 text = fm.elidedText(text: header->text, mode: headerV2->textElideMode, width: rect.width());
1646 }
1647 proxy()->drawItemText(painter: p, rect, flags: header->textAlignment, pal: header->palette,
1648 enabled: header->state.testFlag(flag: State_Enabled), text, textRole: QPalette::ButtonText);
1649 }
1650 break;
1651#if QT_CONFIG(toolbutton)
1652 case CE_ToolButtonLabel:
1653 if (const QStyleOptionToolButton *toolbutton
1654 = qstyleoption_cast<const QStyleOptionToolButton *>(opt)) {
1655 QRect rect = toolbutton->rect;
1656 int shiftX = 0;
1657 int shiftY = 0;
1658 if (toolbutton->state & (State_Sunken | State_On)) {
1659 shiftX = proxy()->pixelMetric(metric: PM_ButtonShiftHorizontal, option: toolbutton, widget);
1660 shiftY = proxy()->pixelMetric(metric: PM_ButtonShiftVertical, option: toolbutton, widget);
1661 }
1662 // Arrow type always overrules and is always shown
1663 bool hasArrow = toolbutton->features & QStyleOptionToolButton::Arrow;
1664 if (((!hasArrow && toolbutton->icon.isNull()) && !toolbutton->text.isEmpty())
1665 || toolbutton->toolButtonStyle == Qt::ToolButtonTextOnly) {
1666 int alignment = Qt::AlignCenter | Qt::TextShowMnemonic;
1667 if (!proxy()->styleHint(stylehint: SH_UnderlineShortcut, opt, widget))
1668 alignment |= Qt::TextHideMnemonic;
1669 rect.translate(dx: shiftX, dy: shiftY);
1670 p->setFont(toolbutton->font);
1671 const QString text = d->toolButtonElideText(option: toolbutton, textRect: rect, flags: alignment);
1672 proxy()->drawItemText(painter: p, rect, flags: alignment, pal: toolbutton->palette,
1673 enabled: opt->state & State_Enabled, text,
1674 textRole: QPalette::ButtonText);
1675 } else {
1676 QPixmap pm;
1677 QSize pmSize = toolbutton->iconSize;
1678 if (!toolbutton->icon.isNull()) {
1679 QIcon::State state = toolbutton->state & State_On ? QIcon::On : QIcon::Off;
1680 QIcon::Mode mode;
1681 if (!(toolbutton->state & State_Enabled))
1682 mode = QIcon::Disabled;
1683 else if ((opt->state & State_MouseOver) && (opt->state & State_AutoRaise))
1684 mode = QIcon::Active;
1685 else
1686 mode = QIcon::Normal;
1687 pm = toolbutton->icon.pixmap(size: toolbutton->rect.size().boundedTo(otherSize: toolbutton->iconSize), devicePixelRatio: p->device()->devicePixelRatio(),
1688 mode, state);
1689 pmSize = pm.size() / pm.devicePixelRatio();
1690 }
1691
1692 if (toolbutton->toolButtonStyle != Qt::ToolButtonIconOnly) {
1693 p->setFont(toolbutton->font);
1694 QRect pr = rect,
1695 tr = rect;
1696 int alignment = Qt::TextShowMnemonic;
1697 if (!proxy()->styleHint(stylehint: SH_UnderlineShortcut, opt, widget))
1698 alignment |= Qt::TextHideMnemonic;
1699
1700 if (toolbutton->toolButtonStyle == Qt::ToolButtonTextUnderIcon) {
1701 pr.setHeight(pmSize.height() + 4); //### 4 is currently hardcoded in QToolButton::sizeHint()
1702 tr.adjust(dx1: 0, dy1: pr.height() - 1, dx2: 0, dy2: -1);
1703 pr.translate(dx: shiftX, dy: shiftY);
1704 if (!hasArrow) {
1705 proxy()->drawItemPixmap(painter: p, rect: pr, alignment: Qt::AlignCenter, pixmap: pm);
1706 } else {
1707 drawArrow(style: proxy(), toolbutton, rect: pr, painter: p, widget);
1708 }
1709 alignment |= Qt::AlignCenter;
1710 } else {
1711 pr.setWidth(pmSize.width() + 4); //### 4 is currently hardcoded in QToolButton::sizeHint()
1712 tr.adjust(dx1: pr.width(), dy1: 0, dx2: 0, dy2: 0);
1713 pr.translate(dx: shiftX, dy: shiftY);
1714 if (!hasArrow) {
1715 proxy()->drawItemPixmap(painter: p, rect: QStyle::visualRect(direction: opt->direction, boundingRect: rect, logicalRect: pr), alignment: Qt::AlignCenter, pixmap: pm);
1716 } else {
1717 drawArrow(style: proxy(), toolbutton, rect: pr, painter: p, widget);
1718 }
1719 alignment |= Qt::AlignLeft | Qt::AlignVCenter;
1720 }
1721 tr.translate(dx: shiftX, dy: shiftY);
1722 const QString text = d->toolButtonElideText(option: toolbutton, textRect: tr, flags: alignment);
1723 proxy()->drawItemText(painter: p, rect: QStyle::visualRect(direction: opt->direction, boundingRect: rect, logicalRect: tr), flags: alignment, pal: toolbutton->palette,
1724 enabled: toolbutton->state & State_Enabled, text,
1725 textRole: QPalette::ButtonText);
1726 } else {
1727 rect.translate(dx: shiftX, dy: shiftY);
1728 if (hasArrow) {
1729 drawArrow(style: proxy(), toolbutton, rect, painter: p, widget);
1730 } else {
1731 proxy()->drawItemPixmap(painter: p, rect, alignment: Qt::AlignCenter, pixmap: pm);
1732 }
1733 }
1734 }
1735 }
1736 break;
1737#endif // QT_CONFIG(toolbutton)
1738#if QT_CONFIG(toolbox)
1739 case CE_ToolBoxTab:
1740 if (const QStyleOptionToolBox *tb = qstyleoption_cast<const QStyleOptionToolBox *>(opt)) {
1741 proxy()->drawControl(element: CE_ToolBoxTabShape, opt: tb, p, w: widget);
1742 proxy()->drawControl(element: CE_ToolBoxTabLabel, opt: tb, p, w: widget);
1743 }
1744 break;
1745 case CE_ToolBoxTabShape:
1746 if (const QStyleOptionToolBox *tb = qstyleoption_cast<const QStyleOptionToolBox *>(opt)) {
1747 p->setPen(tb->palette.mid().color().darker(f: 150));
1748 int d = 20 + tb->rect.height() - 3;
1749 if (tb->direction != Qt::RightToLeft) {
1750 const QPoint points[] = {
1751 QPoint(-1, tb->rect.height() + 1),
1752 QPoint(-1, 1),
1753 QPoint(tb->rect.width() - d, 1),
1754 QPoint(tb->rect.width() - 20, tb->rect.height() - 2),
1755 QPoint(tb->rect.width() - 1, tb->rect.height() - 2),
1756 QPoint(tb->rect.width() - 1, tb->rect.height() + 1),
1757 QPoint(-1, tb->rect.height() + 1),
1758 };
1759 p->drawPolygon(points, pointCount: sizeof points / sizeof *points);
1760 } else {
1761 const QPoint points[] = {
1762 QPoint(tb->rect.width(), tb->rect.height() + 1),
1763 QPoint(tb->rect.width(), 1),
1764 QPoint(d - 1, 1),
1765 QPoint(20 - 1, tb->rect.height() - 2),
1766 QPoint(0, tb->rect.height() - 2),
1767 QPoint(0, tb->rect.height() + 1),
1768 QPoint(tb->rect.width(), tb->rect.height() + 1),
1769 };
1770 p->drawPolygon(points, pointCount: sizeof points / sizeof *points);
1771 }
1772 p->setPen(tb->palette.light().color());
1773 if (tb->direction != Qt::RightToLeft) {
1774 p->drawLine(x1: 0, y1: 2, x2: tb->rect.width() - d, y2: 2);
1775 p->drawLine(x1: tb->rect.width() - d - 1, y1: 2, x2: tb->rect.width() - 21, y2: tb->rect.height() - 1);
1776 p->drawLine(x1: tb->rect.width() - 20, y1: tb->rect.height() - 1,
1777 x2: tb->rect.width(), y2: tb->rect.height() - 1);
1778 } else {
1779 p->drawLine(x1: tb->rect.width() - 1, y1: 2, x2: d - 1, y2: 2);
1780 p->drawLine(x1: d, y1: 2, x2: 20, y2: tb->rect.height() - 1);
1781 p->drawLine(x1: 19, y1: tb->rect.height() - 1,
1782 x2: -1, y2: tb->rect.height() - 1);
1783 }
1784 p->setBrush(Qt::NoBrush);
1785 }
1786 break;
1787#endif // QT_CONFIG(toolbox)
1788#if QT_CONFIG(tabbar)
1789 case CE_TabBarTab:
1790 if (const QStyleOptionTab *tab = qstyleoption_cast<const QStyleOptionTab *>(opt)) {
1791 proxy()->drawControl(element: CE_TabBarTabShape, opt: tab, p, w: widget);
1792 proxy()->drawControl(element: CE_TabBarTabLabel, opt: tab, p, w: widget);
1793 }
1794 break;
1795 case CE_TabBarTabShape:
1796 if (const QStyleOptionTab *tab = qstyleoption_cast<const QStyleOptionTab *>(opt)) {
1797 p->save();
1798
1799 QRect rect(tab->rect);
1800 bool selected = tab->state & State_Selected;
1801 bool onlyOne = tab->position == QStyleOptionTab::OnlyOneTab;
1802 int tabOverlap = onlyOne ? 0 : proxy()->pixelMetric(metric: PM_TabBarTabOverlap, option: opt, widget);
1803
1804 if (!selected) {
1805 switch (tab->shape) {
1806 case QTabBar::TriangularNorth:
1807 rect.adjust(dx1: 0, dy1: 0, dx2: 0, dy2: -tabOverlap);
1808 if (!selected)
1809 rect.adjust(dx1: 1, dy1: 1, dx2: -1, dy2: 0);
1810 break;
1811 case QTabBar::TriangularSouth:
1812 rect.adjust(dx1: 0, dy1: tabOverlap, dx2: 0, dy2: 0);
1813 if (!selected)
1814 rect.adjust(dx1: 1, dy1: 0, dx2: -1, dy2: -1);
1815 break;
1816 case QTabBar::TriangularEast:
1817 rect.adjust(dx1: tabOverlap, dy1: 0, dx2: 0, dy2: 0);
1818 if (!selected)
1819 rect.adjust(dx1: 0, dy1: 1, dx2: -1, dy2: -1);
1820 break;
1821 case QTabBar::TriangularWest:
1822 rect.adjust(dx1: 0, dy1: 0, dx2: -tabOverlap, dy2: 0);
1823 if (!selected)
1824 rect.adjust(dx1: 1, dy1: 1, dx2: 0, dy2: -1);
1825 break;
1826 default:
1827 break;
1828 }
1829 }
1830
1831 p->setPen(QPen(tab->palette.windowText(), 0));
1832 if (selected) {
1833 p->setBrush(tab->palette.base());
1834 } else {
1835 if (widget && widget->parentWidget())
1836 p->setBrush(widget->parentWidget()->palette().window());
1837 else
1838 p->setBrush(tab->palette.window());
1839 }
1840
1841 int y;
1842 int x;
1843 QPolygon a(10);
1844 switch (tab->shape) {
1845 case QTabBar::TriangularNorth:
1846 case QTabBar::TriangularSouth: {
1847 a.setPoint(index: 0, x: 0, y: -1);
1848 a.setPoint(index: 1, x: 0, y: 0);
1849 y = rect.height() - 2;
1850 x = y / 3;
1851 a.setPoint(index: 2, x: x++, y: y - 1);
1852 ++x;
1853 a.setPoint(index: 3, x: x++, y: y++);
1854 a.setPoint(index: 4, x, y);
1855
1856 int i;
1857 int right = rect.width() - 1;
1858 for (i = 0; i < 5; ++i)
1859 a.setPoint(index: 9 - i, x: right - a.point(index: i).x(), y: a.point(index: i).y());
1860 if (tab->shape == QTabBar::TriangularNorth)
1861 for (i = 0; i < 10; ++i)
1862 a.setPoint(index: i, x: a.point(index: i).x(), y: rect.height() - 1 - a.point(index: i).y());
1863
1864 a.translate(dx: rect.left(), dy: rect.top());
1865 p->setRenderHint(hint: QPainter::Antialiasing);
1866 p->translate(dx: 0, dy: 0.5);
1867
1868 QPainterPath path;
1869 path.addPolygon(polygon: a);
1870 p->drawPath(path);
1871 break; }
1872 case QTabBar::TriangularEast:
1873 case QTabBar::TriangularWest: {
1874 a.setPoint(index: 0, x: -1, y: 0);
1875 a.setPoint(index: 1, x: 0, y: 0);
1876 x = rect.width() - 2;
1877 y = x / 3;
1878 a.setPoint(index: 2, x: x - 1, y: y++);
1879 ++y;
1880 a.setPoint(index: 3, x: x++, y: y++);
1881 a.setPoint(index: 4, x, y);
1882 int i;
1883 int bottom = rect.height() - 1;
1884 for (i = 0; i < 5; ++i)
1885 a.setPoint(index: 9 - i, x: a.point(index: i).x(), y: bottom - a.point(index: i).y());
1886 if (tab->shape == QTabBar::TriangularWest)
1887 for (i = 0; i < 10; ++i)
1888 a.setPoint(index: i, x: rect.width() - 1 - a.point(index: i).x(), y: a.point(index: i).y());
1889 a.translate(dx: rect.left(), dy: rect.top());
1890 p->setRenderHint(hint: QPainter::Antialiasing);
1891 p->translate(dx: 0.5, dy: 0);
1892 QPainterPath path;
1893 path.addPolygon(polygon: a);
1894 p->drawPath(path);
1895 break; }
1896 default:
1897 break;
1898 }
1899 p->restore();
1900 }
1901 break;
1902 case CE_ToolBoxTabLabel:
1903 if (const QStyleOptionToolBox *tb = qstyleoption_cast<const QStyleOptionToolBox *>(opt)) {
1904 bool enabled = tb->state & State_Enabled;
1905 bool selected = tb->state & State_Selected;
1906 int iconExtent = proxy()->pixelMetric(metric: QStyle::PM_SmallIconSize, option: tb, widget);
1907 QPixmap pm = tb->icon.pixmap(size: QSize(iconExtent, iconExtent), devicePixelRatio: p->device()->devicePixelRatio(),
1908 mode: enabled ? QIcon::Normal : QIcon::Disabled);
1909
1910 QRect cr = subElementRect(r: QStyle::SE_ToolBoxTabContents, opt: tb, widget);
1911 QRect tr, ir;
1912 int ih = 0;
1913 if (pm.isNull()) {
1914 tr = cr;
1915 tr.adjust(dx1: 4, dy1: 0, dx2: -8, dy2: 0);
1916 } else {
1917 int iw = pm.width() / pm.devicePixelRatio() + 4;
1918 ih = pm.height()/ pm.devicePixelRatio();
1919 ir = QRect(cr.left() + 4, cr.top(), iw + 2, ih);
1920 tr = QRect(ir.right(), cr.top(), cr.width() - ir.right() - 4, cr.height());
1921 }
1922
1923 if (selected && proxy()->styleHint(stylehint: QStyle::SH_ToolBox_SelectedPageTitleBold, opt: tb, widget)) {
1924 QFont f(p->font());
1925 f.setBold(true);
1926 p->setFont(f);
1927 }
1928
1929 QString txt = tb->fontMetrics.elidedText(text: tb->text, mode: Qt::ElideRight, width: tr.width());
1930
1931 if (ih)
1932 p->drawPixmap(x: ir.left(), y: (tb->rect.height() - ih) / 2, pm);
1933
1934 int alignment = Qt::AlignLeft | Qt::AlignVCenter | Qt::TextShowMnemonic;
1935 if (!proxy()->styleHint(stylehint: QStyle::SH_UnderlineShortcut, opt: tb, widget))
1936 alignment |= Qt::TextHideMnemonic;
1937 proxy()->drawItemText(painter: p, rect: tr, flags: alignment, pal: tb->palette, enabled, text: txt, textRole: QPalette::ButtonText);
1938
1939 if (!txt.isEmpty() && opt->state & State_HasFocus) {
1940 QStyleOptionFocusRect opt;
1941 opt.rect = tr;
1942 opt.palette = tb->palette;
1943 opt.state = QStyle::State_None;
1944 proxy()->drawPrimitive(pe: QStyle::PE_FrameFocusRect, opt: &opt, p, w: widget);
1945 }
1946 }
1947 break;
1948 case CE_TabBarTabLabel:
1949 if (const QStyleOptionTab *tab = qstyleoption_cast<const QStyleOptionTab *>(opt)) {
1950 QRect tr = tab->rect;
1951 bool verticalTabs = tab->shape == QTabBar::RoundedEast
1952 || tab->shape == QTabBar::RoundedWest
1953 || tab->shape == QTabBar::TriangularEast
1954 || tab->shape == QTabBar::TriangularWest;
1955
1956 int alignment = Qt::AlignCenter | Qt::TextShowMnemonic;
1957 if (!proxy()->styleHint(stylehint: SH_UnderlineShortcut, opt, widget))
1958 alignment |= Qt::TextHideMnemonic;
1959
1960 if (verticalTabs) {
1961 p->save();
1962 int newX, newY, newRot;
1963 if (tab->shape == QTabBar::RoundedEast || tab->shape == QTabBar::TriangularEast) {
1964 newX = tr.width() + tr.x();
1965 newY = tr.y();
1966 newRot = 90;
1967 } else {
1968 newX = tr.x();
1969 newY = tr.y() + tr.height();
1970 newRot = -90;
1971 }
1972 QTransform m = QTransform::fromTranslate(dx: newX, dy: newY);
1973 m.rotate(a: newRot);
1974 p->setTransform(transform: m, combine: true);
1975 }
1976 QRect iconRect;
1977 d->tabLayout(opt: tab, widget, textRect: &tr, iconRect: &iconRect);
1978 tr = proxy()->subElementRect(subElement: SE_TabBarTabText, option: opt, widget); //we compute tr twice because the style may override subElementRect
1979
1980 if (!tab->icon.isNull()) {
1981 QPixmap tabIcon = tab->icon.pixmap(size: tab->iconSize, devicePixelRatio: p->device()->devicePixelRatio(),
1982 mode: (tab->state & State_Enabled) ? QIcon::Normal
1983 : QIcon::Disabled,
1984 state: (tab->state & State_Selected) ? QIcon::On
1985 : QIcon::Off);
1986 p->drawPixmap(x: iconRect.x(), y: iconRect.y(), pm: tabIcon);
1987 }
1988
1989 proxy()->drawItemText(painter: p, rect: tr, flags: alignment, pal: tab->palette, enabled: tab->state & State_Enabled, text: tab->text,
1990 textRole: widget ? widget->foregroundRole() : QPalette::WindowText);
1991 if (verticalTabs)
1992 p->restore();
1993
1994 if (tab->state & State_HasFocus) {
1995 const int OFFSET = 1 + pixelMetric(m: PM_DefaultFrameWidth);
1996
1997 int x1, x2;
1998 x1 = tab->rect.left();
1999 x2 = tab->rect.right() - 1;
2000
2001 QStyleOptionFocusRect fropt;
2002 fropt.QStyleOption::operator=(other: *tab);
2003 fropt.rect.setRect(ax: x1 + 1 + OFFSET, ay: tab->rect.y() + OFFSET,
2004 aw: x2 - x1 - 2*OFFSET, ah: tab->rect.height() - 2*OFFSET);
2005 drawPrimitive(pe: PE_FrameFocusRect, opt: &fropt, p, widget);
2006 }
2007 }
2008 break;
2009#endif // QT_CONFIG(tabbar)
2010#if QT_CONFIG(sizegrip)
2011 case CE_SizeGrip: {
2012 p->save();
2013 int x, y, w, h;
2014 opt->rect.getRect(ax: &x, ay: &y, aw: &w, ah: &h);
2015
2016 int sw = qMin(a: h, b: w);
2017 if (h > w)
2018 p->translate(dx: 0, dy: h - w);
2019 else
2020 p->translate(dx: w - h, dy: 0);
2021
2022 int sx = x;
2023 int sy = y;
2024 int s = sw / 3;
2025
2026 Qt::Corner corner;
2027 if (const QStyleOptionSizeGrip *sgOpt = qstyleoption_cast<const QStyleOptionSizeGrip *>(opt))
2028 corner = sgOpt->corner;
2029 else if (opt->direction == Qt::RightToLeft)
2030 corner = Qt::BottomLeftCorner;
2031 else
2032 corner = Qt::BottomRightCorner;
2033
2034 if (corner == Qt::BottomLeftCorner) {
2035 sx = x + sw;
2036 for (int i = 0; i < 4; ++i) {
2037 p->setPen(QPen(opt->palette.light().color(), 1));
2038 p->drawLine(x1: x, y1: sy - 1 , x2: sx + 1, y2: sw);
2039 p->setPen(QPen(opt->palette.dark().color(), 1));
2040 p->drawLine(x1: x, y1: sy, x2: sx, y2: sw);
2041 p->setPen(QPen(opt->palette.dark().color(), 1));
2042 p->drawLine(x1: x, y1: sy + 1, x2: sx - 1, y2: sw);
2043 sx -= s;
2044 sy += s;
2045 }
2046 } else if (corner == Qt::BottomRightCorner) {
2047 for (int i = 0; i < 4; ++i) {
2048 p->setPen(QPen(opt->palette.light().color(), 1));
2049 p->drawLine(x1: sx - 1, y1: sw, x2: sw, y2: sy - 1);
2050 p->setPen(QPen(opt->palette.dark().color(), 1));
2051 p->drawLine(x1: sx, y1: sw, x2: sw, y2: sy);
2052 p->setPen(QPen(opt->palette.dark().color(), 1));
2053 p->drawLine(x1: sx + 1, y1: sw, x2: sw, y2: sy + 1);
2054 sx += s;
2055 sy += s;
2056 }
2057 } else if (corner == Qt::TopRightCorner) {
2058 sy = y + sw;
2059 for (int i = 0; i < 4; ++i) {
2060 p->setPen(QPen(opt->palette.light().color(), 1));
2061 p->drawLine(x1: sx - 1, y1: y, x2: sw, y2: sy + 1);
2062 p->setPen(QPen(opt->palette.dark().color(), 1));
2063 p->drawLine(x1: sx, y1: y, x2: sw, y2: sy);
2064 p->setPen(QPen(opt->palette.dark().color(), 1));
2065 p->drawLine(x1: sx + 1, y1: y, x2: sw, y2: sy - 1);
2066 sx += s;
2067 sy -= s;
2068 }
2069 } else if (corner == Qt::TopLeftCorner) {
2070 for (int i = 0; i < 4; ++i) {
2071 p->setPen(QPen(opt->palette.light().color(), 1));
2072 p->drawLine(x1: x, y1: sy - 1, x2: sx - 1, y2: y);
2073 p->setPen(QPen(opt->palette.dark().color(), 1));
2074 p->drawLine(x1: x, y1: sy, x2: sx, y2: y);
2075 p->setPen(QPen(opt->palette.dark().color(), 1));
2076 p->drawLine(x1: x, y1: sy + 1, x2: sx + 1, y2: y);
2077 sx += s;
2078 sy += s;
2079 }
2080 }
2081 p->restore();
2082 break; }
2083#endif // QT_CONFIG(sizegrip)
2084#if QT_CONFIG(rubberband)
2085 case CE_RubberBand: {
2086 if (const QStyleOptionRubberBand *rbOpt = qstyleoption_cast<const QStyleOptionRubberBand *>(opt)) {
2087 QPixmap tiledPixmap(16, 16);
2088 QPainter pixmapPainter(&tiledPixmap);
2089 pixmapPainter.setPen(Qt::NoPen);
2090 pixmapPainter.setBrush(Qt::Dense4Pattern);
2091 pixmapPainter.setBackground(QBrush(opt->palette.base()));
2092 pixmapPainter.setBackgroundMode(Qt::OpaqueMode);
2093 pixmapPainter.drawRect(x: 0, y: 0, w: tiledPixmap.width(), h: tiledPixmap.height());
2094 pixmapPainter.end();
2095 // ### workaround for borked XRENDER
2096 tiledPixmap = QPixmap::fromImage(image: tiledPixmap.toImage());
2097
2098 p->save();
2099 QRect r = opt->rect;
2100 QStyleHintReturnMask mask;
2101 if (proxy()->styleHint(stylehint: QStyle::SH_RubberBand_Mask, opt, widget, returnData: &mask))
2102 p->setClipRegion(mask.region);
2103 p->drawTiledPixmap(x: r.x(), y: r.y(), w: r.width(), h: r.height(), pm: tiledPixmap);
2104 p->setPen(opt->palette.color(cg: QPalette::Active, cr: QPalette::WindowText));
2105 p->setBrush(Qt::NoBrush);
2106 p->drawRect(r: r.adjusted(xp1: 0, yp1: 0, xp2: -1, yp2: -1));
2107 if (rbOpt->shape == QRubberBand::Rectangle)
2108 p->drawRect(r: r.adjusted(xp1: 3, yp1: 3, xp2: -4, yp2: -4));
2109 p->restore();
2110 }
2111 break; }
2112#endif // QT_CONFIG(rubberband)
2113#if QT_CONFIG(dockwidget)
2114 case CE_DockWidgetTitle:
2115 if (const QStyleOptionDockWidget *dwOpt = qstyleoption_cast<const QStyleOptionDockWidget *>(opt)) {
2116 QRect r = dwOpt->rect.adjusted(xp1: 0, yp1: 0, xp2: -1, yp2: -1);
2117 if (dwOpt->movable) {
2118 p->setPen(dwOpt->palette.color(cr: QPalette::Dark));
2119 p->drawRect(r);
2120 }
2121
2122 if (!dwOpt->title.isEmpty()) {
2123 const bool verticalTitleBar = dwOpt->verticalTitleBar;
2124
2125 if (verticalTitleBar) {
2126 r = r.transposed();
2127
2128 p->save();
2129 p->translate(dx: r.left(), dy: r.top() + r.width());
2130 p->rotate(a: -90);
2131 p->translate(dx: -r.left(), dy: -r.top());
2132 }
2133
2134 const int indent = p->fontMetrics().descent();
2135 proxy()->drawItemText(painter: p, rect: r.adjusted(xp1: indent + 1, yp1: 1, xp2: -indent - 1, yp2: -1),
2136 flags: Qt::AlignLeft | Qt::AlignVCenter, pal: dwOpt->palette,
2137 enabled: dwOpt->state & State_Enabled, text: dwOpt->title,
2138 textRole: QPalette::WindowText);
2139
2140 if (verticalTitleBar)
2141 p->restore();
2142 }
2143 }
2144 break;
2145#endif // QT_CONFIG(dockwidget)
2146 case CE_Header:
2147 if (const QStyleOptionHeader *header = qstyleoption_cast<const QStyleOptionHeader *>(opt)) {
2148 QRegion clipRegion = p->clipRegion();
2149 p->setClipRect(opt->rect);
2150 proxy()->drawControl(element: CE_HeaderSection, opt: header, p, w: widget);
2151 QStyleOptionHeader subopt = *header;
2152 subopt.rect = subElementRect(r: SE_HeaderLabel, opt: header, widget);
2153 if (subopt.rect.isValid())
2154 proxy()->drawControl(element: CE_HeaderLabel, opt: &subopt, p, w: widget);
2155 if (header->sortIndicator != QStyleOptionHeader::None) {
2156 subopt.rect = subElementRect(r: SE_HeaderArrow, opt, widget);
2157 proxy()->drawPrimitive(pe: PE_IndicatorHeaderArrow, opt: &subopt, p, w: widget);
2158 }
2159 p->setClipRegion(clipRegion);
2160 }
2161 break;
2162 case CE_FocusFrame:
2163 p->fillRect(opt->rect, opt->palette.windowText());
2164 break;
2165 case CE_HeaderSection:
2166 qDrawShadePanel(p, r: opt->rect, pal: opt->palette,
2167 sunken: opt->state & State_Sunken, lineWidth: 1,
2168 fill: &opt->palette.brush(cr: QPalette::Button));
2169 break;
2170 case CE_HeaderEmptyArea:
2171 p->fillRect(opt->rect, opt->palette.window());
2172 break;
2173#if QT_CONFIG(combobox)
2174 case CE_ComboBoxLabel:
2175 if (const QStyleOptionComboBox *cb = qstyleoption_cast<const QStyleOptionComboBox *>(opt)) {
2176 QRect editRect = proxy()->subControlRect(cc: CC_ComboBox, opt: cb, sc: SC_ComboBoxEditField, widget);
2177 p->save();
2178 p->setClipRect(editRect);
2179 if (!cb->currentIcon.isNull()) {
2180 QIcon::Mode mode = cb->state & State_Enabled ? QIcon::Normal
2181 : QIcon::Disabled;
2182 QPixmap pixmap = cb->currentIcon.pixmap(size: cb->iconSize, devicePixelRatio: p->device()->devicePixelRatio(), mode);
2183 QRect iconRect(editRect);
2184 iconRect.setWidth(cb->iconSize.width() + 4);
2185 iconRect = alignedRect(direction: cb->direction,
2186 alignment: Qt::AlignLeft | Qt::AlignVCenter,
2187 size: iconRect.size(), rectangle: editRect);
2188 if (cb->editable)
2189 p->fillRect(iconRect, opt->palette.brush(cr: QPalette::Base));
2190 proxy()->drawItemPixmap(painter: p, rect: iconRect, alignment: Qt::AlignCenter, pixmap);
2191
2192 if (cb->direction == Qt::RightToLeft)
2193 editRect.translate(dx: -4 - cb->iconSize.width(), dy: 0);
2194 else
2195 editRect.translate(dx: cb->iconSize.width() + 4, dy: 0);
2196 }
2197 if (!cb->currentText.isEmpty() && !cb->editable) {
2198 proxy()->drawItemText(painter: p, rect: editRect.adjusted(xp1: 1, yp1: 0, xp2: -1, yp2: 0),
2199 flags: visualAlignment(direction: cb->direction, alignment: cb->textAlignment),
2200 pal: cb->palette, enabled: cb->state & State_Enabled, text: cb->currentText);
2201 }
2202 p->restore();
2203 }
2204 break;
2205#endif // QT_CONFIG(combobox)
2206#if QT_CONFIG(toolbar)
2207 case CE_ToolBar:
2208 if (const QStyleOptionToolBar *toolBar = qstyleoption_cast<const QStyleOptionToolBar *>(opt)) {
2209 // Compatibility with styles that use PE_PanelToolBar
2210 QStyleOptionFrame frame;
2211 frame.QStyleOption::operator=(other: *toolBar);
2212 frame.lineWidth = toolBar->lineWidth;
2213 frame.midLineWidth = toolBar->midLineWidth;
2214 proxy()->drawPrimitive(pe: PE_PanelToolBar, opt, p, w: widget);
2215
2216 if (widget && qobject_cast<QToolBar *>(object: widget->parentWidget()))
2217 break;
2218 qDrawShadePanel(p, r: toolBar->rect, pal: toolBar->palette, sunken: false, lineWidth: toolBar->lineWidth,
2219 fill: &toolBar->palette.brush(cr: QPalette::Button));
2220 }
2221 break;
2222#endif // QT_CONFIG(toolbar)
2223 case CE_ColumnViewGrip: {
2224 // draw background gradients
2225 QLinearGradient g(0, 0, opt->rect.width(), 0);
2226 g.setColorAt(pos: 0, color: opt->palette.color(cg: QPalette::Active, cr: QPalette::Mid));
2227 g.setColorAt(pos: 0.5, color: Qt::white);
2228 p->fillRect(QRect(0, 0, opt->rect.width(), opt->rect.height()), g);
2229
2230 // draw the two lines
2231 QPen pen(p->pen());
2232 pen.setWidth(opt->rect.width()/20);
2233 pen.setColor(opt->palette.color(cg: QPalette::Active, cr: QPalette::Dark));
2234 p->setPen(pen);
2235
2236 int line1starting = opt->rect.width()*8 / 20;
2237 int line2starting = opt->rect.width()*13 / 20;
2238 int top = opt->rect.height()*20/75;
2239 int bottom = opt->rect.height() - 1 - top;
2240 p->drawLine(x1: line1starting, y1: top, x2: line1starting, y2: bottom);
2241 p->drawLine(x1: line2starting, y1: top, x2: line2starting, y2: bottom);
2242 }
2243 break;
2244
2245#if QT_CONFIG(itemviews)
2246 case CE_ItemViewItem:
2247 if (const QStyleOptionViewItem *vopt = qstyleoption_cast<const QStyleOptionViewItem *>(opt)) {
2248 p->save();
2249 // the style calling this might want to clip, so respect any region already set
2250 const QRegion clipRegion = p->hasClipping() ? (p->clipRegion() & opt->rect) : opt->rect;
2251 p->setClipRegion(clipRegion);
2252
2253 QRect checkRect = proxy()->subElementRect(subElement: SE_ItemViewItemCheckIndicator, option: vopt, widget);
2254 QRect iconRect = proxy()->subElementRect(subElement: SE_ItemViewItemDecoration, option: vopt, widget);
2255 QRect textRect = proxy()->subElementRect(subElement: SE_ItemViewItemText, option: vopt, widget);
2256
2257 // draw the background
2258 proxy()->drawPrimitive(pe: PE_PanelItemViewItem, opt, p, w: widget);
2259
2260 // draw the check mark
2261 if (vopt->features & QStyleOptionViewItem::HasCheckIndicator) {
2262 QStyleOptionViewItem option(*vopt);
2263 option.rect = checkRect;
2264 option.state = option.state & ~QStyle::State_HasFocus;
2265
2266 switch (vopt->checkState) {
2267 case Qt::Unchecked:
2268 option.state |= QStyle::State_Off;
2269 break;
2270 case Qt::PartiallyChecked:
2271 option.state |= QStyle::State_NoChange;
2272 break;
2273 case Qt::Checked:
2274 option.state |= QStyle::State_On;
2275 break;
2276 }
2277 proxy()->drawPrimitive(pe: QStyle::PE_IndicatorItemViewItemCheck, opt: &option, p, w: widget);
2278 }
2279
2280 // draw the icon
2281 QIcon::Mode mode = QIcon::Normal;
2282 if (!(vopt->state & QStyle::State_Enabled))
2283 mode = QIcon::Disabled;
2284 else if (vopt->state & QStyle::State_Selected)
2285 mode = QIcon::Selected;
2286 QIcon::State state = vopt->state & QStyle::State_Open ? QIcon::On : QIcon::Off;
2287 vopt->icon.paint(painter: p, rect: iconRect, alignment: vopt->decorationAlignment, mode, state);
2288
2289 // draw the text
2290 if (!vopt->text.isEmpty()) {
2291 QPalette::ColorGroup cg = vopt->state & QStyle::State_Enabled
2292 ? QPalette::Normal : QPalette::Disabled;
2293 if (cg == QPalette::Normal && !(vopt->state & QStyle::State_Active))
2294 cg = QPalette::Inactive;
2295
2296 if (vopt->state & QStyle::State_Selected) {
2297 p->setPen(vopt->palette.color(cg, cr: QPalette::HighlightedText));
2298 } else {
2299 p->setPen(vopt->palette.color(cg, cr: QPalette::Text));
2300 }
2301 if (vopt->state & QStyle::State_Editing) {
2302 p->setPen(vopt->palette.color(cg, cr: QPalette::Text));
2303 p->drawRect(r: textRect.adjusted(xp1: 0, yp1: 0, xp2: -1, yp2: -1));
2304 }
2305
2306 d->viewItemDrawText(p, option: vopt, rect: textRect);
2307 }
2308
2309 // draw the focus rect
2310 if (vopt->state & QStyle::State_HasFocus) {
2311 QStyleOptionFocusRect o;
2312 o.QStyleOption::operator=(other: *vopt);
2313 o.rect = proxy()->subElementRect(subElement: SE_ItemViewItemFocusRect, option: vopt, widget);
2314 o.state |= QStyle::State_KeyboardFocusChange;
2315 o.state |= QStyle::State_Item;
2316 QPalette::ColorGroup cg = (vopt->state & QStyle::State_Enabled)
2317 ? QPalette::Normal : QPalette::Disabled;
2318 o.backgroundColor = vopt->palette.color(cg, cr: (vopt->state & QStyle::State_Selected)
2319 ? QPalette::Highlight : QPalette::Window);
2320 proxy()->drawPrimitive(pe: QStyle::PE_FrameFocusRect, opt: &o, p, w: widget);
2321 }
2322
2323 p->restore();
2324 }
2325 break;
2326
2327#endif // QT_CONFIG(itemviews)
2328#ifndef QT_NO_FRAME
2329 case CE_ShapedFrame:
2330 if (const QStyleOptionFrame *f = qstyleoption_cast<const QStyleOptionFrame *>(opt)) {
2331 int frameShape = f->frameShape;
2332 int frameShadow = QFrame::Plain;
2333 if (f->state & QStyle::State_Sunken) {
2334 frameShadow = QFrame::Sunken;
2335 } else if (f->state & QStyle::State_Raised) {
2336 frameShadow = QFrame::Raised;
2337 }
2338
2339 int lw = f->lineWidth;
2340 int mlw = f->midLineWidth;
2341 QPalette::ColorRole foregroundRole = QPalette::WindowText;
2342 if (widget)
2343 foregroundRole = widget->foregroundRole();
2344
2345 switch (frameShape) {
2346 case QFrame::Box:
2347 if (frameShadow == QFrame::Plain) {
2348 qDrawPlainRect(p, r: f->rect, f->palette.color(cr: foregroundRole), lineWidth: lw);
2349 } else {
2350 qDrawShadeRect(p, r: f->rect, pal: f->palette, sunken: frameShadow == QFrame::Sunken, lineWidth: lw, midLineWidth: mlw);
2351 }
2352 break;
2353 case QFrame::StyledPanel:
2354 //keep the compatibility with Qt 4.4 if there is a proxy style.
2355 //be sure to call drawPrimitive(QStyle::PE_Frame) on the proxy style
2356 if (widget) {
2357 widget->style()->drawPrimitive(pe: QStyle::PE_Frame, opt, p, w: widget);
2358 } else {
2359 proxy()->drawPrimitive(pe: QStyle::PE_Frame, opt, p, w: widget);
2360 }
2361 break;
2362 case QFrame::Panel:
2363 if (frameShadow == QFrame::Plain) {
2364 qDrawPlainRect(p, r: f->rect, f->palette.color(cr: foregroundRole), lineWidth: lw);
2365 } else {
2366 qDrawShadePanel(p, r: f->rect, pal: f->palette, sunken: frameShadow == QFrame::Sunken, lineWidth: lw);
2367 }
2368 break;
2369 case QFrame::WinPanel:
2370 if (frameShadow == QFrame::Plain) {
2371 qDrawPlainRect(p, r: f->rect, f->palette.color(cr: foregroundRole), lineWidth: lw);
2372 } else {
2373 qDrawWinPanel(p, r: f->rect, pal: f->palette, sunken: frameShadow == QFrame::Sunken);
2374 }
2375 break;
2376 case QFrame::HLine:
2377 case QFrame::VLine: {
2378 QPoint p1, p2;
2379 if (frameShape == QFrame::HLine) {
2380 p1 = QPoint(opt->rect.x(), opt->rect.y() + opt->rect.height() / 2);
2381 p2 = QPoint(opt->rect.x() + opt->rect.width(), p1.y());
2382 } else {
2383 p1 = QPoint(opt->rect.x() + opt->rect.width() / 2, opt->rect.y());
2384 p2 = QPoint(p1.x(), p1.y() + opt->rect.height());
2385 }
2386 if (frameShadow == QFrame::Plain) {
2387 QPen oldPen = p->pen();
2388 p->setPen(QPen(opt->palette.brush(cr: foregroundRole), lw));
2389 p->drawLine(p1, p2);
2390 p->setPen(oldPen);
2391 } else {
2392 qDrawShadeLine(p, p1, p2, pal: f->palette, sunken: frameShadow == QFrame::Sunken, lineWidth: lw, midLineWidth: mlw);
2393 }
2394 break;
2395 }
2396 }
2397 }
2398 break;
2399#endif
2400 default:
2401 break;
2402 }
2403#if !QT_CONFIG(tabbar) && !QT_CONFIG(itemviews)
2404 Q_UNUSED(d);
2405#endif
2406}
2407
2408/*!
2409 \reimp
2410*/
2411QRect QCommonStyle::subElementRect(SubElement sr, const QStyleOption *opt,
2412 const QWidget *widget) const
2413{
2414 Q_D(const QCommonStyle);
2415 QRect r;
2416 switch (sr) {
2417 case SE_PushButtonContents:
2418 if (const QStyleOptionButton *btn = qstyleoption_cast<const QStyleOptionButton *>(opt)) {
2419 int dx1, dx2;
2420 dx1 = proxy()->pixelMetric(metric: PM_DefaultFrameWidth, option: btn, widget);
2421 if (btn->features & QStyleOptionButton::AutoDefaultButton)
2422 dx1 += proxy()->pixelMetric(metric: PM_ButtonDefaultIndicator, option: btn, widget);
2423 dx2 = dx1 * 2;
2424 r.setRect(ax: opt->rect.x() + dx1, ay: opt->rect.y() + dx1, aw: opt->rect.width() - dx2,
2425 ah: opt->rect.height() - dx2);
2426 r = visualRect(direction: opt->direction, boundingRect: opt->rect, logicalRect: r);
2427 }
2428 break;
2429 case SE_PushButtonFocusRect:
2430 if (const QStyleOptionButton *btn = qstyleoption_cast<const QStyleOptionButton *>(opt)) {
2431 int dbw1 = 0, dbw2 = 0;
2432 if (btn->features & QStyleOptionButton::AutoDefaultButton){
2433 dbw1 = proxy()->pixelMetric(metric: PM_ButtonDefaultIndicator, option: btn, widget);
2434 dbw2 = dbw1 * 2;
2435 }
2436
2437 int dfw1 = proxy()->pixelMetric(metric: PM_DefaultFrameWidth, option: btn, widget) + 1,
2438 dfw2 = dfw1 * 2;
2439
2440 r.setRect(ax: btn->rect.x() + dfw1 + dbw1, ay: btn->rect.y() + dfw1 + dbw1,
2441 aw: btn->rect.width() - dfw2 - dbw2, ah: btn->rect.height()- dfw2 - dbw2);
2442 r = visualRect(direction: opt->direction, boundingRect: opt->rect, logicalRect: r);
2443 }
2444 break;
2445 case SE_PushButtonBevel:
2446 {
2447 r = opt->rect;
2448 r = visualRect(direction: opt->direction, boundingRect: opt->rect, logicalRect: r);
2449 }
2450 break;
2451 case SE_CheckBoxIndicator:
2452 {
2453 int h = proxy()->pixelMetric(metric: PM_IndicatorHeight, option: opt, widget);
2454 r.setRect(ax: opt->rect.x(), ay: opt->rect.y() + ((opt->rect.height() - h) / 2),
2455 aw: proxy()->pixelMetric(metric: PM_IndicatorWidth, option: opt, widget), ah: h);
2456 r = visualRect(direction: opt->direction, boundingRect: opt->rect, logicalRect: r);
2457 }
2458 break;
2459
2460 case SE_CheckBoxContents:
2461 {
2462 // Deal with the logical first, then convert it back to screen coords.
2463 QRect ir = visualRect(direction: opt->direction, boundingRect: opt->rect,
2464 logicalRect: subElementRect(sr: SE_CheckBoxIndicator, opt, widget));
2465 int spacing = proxy()->pixelMetric(metric: PM_CheckBoxLabelSpacing, option: opt, widget);
2466 r.setRect(ax: ir.right() + spacing, ay: opt->rect.y(), aw: opt->rect.width() - ir.width() - spacing,
2467 ah: opt->rect.height());
2468 r = visualRect(direction: opt->direction, boundingRect: opt->rect, logicalRect: r);
2469 }
2470 break;
2471
2472 case SE_CheckBoxFocusRect:
2473 if (const QStyleOptionButton *btn = qstyleoption_cast<const QStyleOptionButton *>(opt)) {
2474 if (btn->icon.isNull() && btn->text.isEmpty()) {
2475 r = subElementRect(sr: SE_CheckBoxIndicator, opt, widget);
2476 r.adjust(dx1: 1, dy1: 1, dx2: -1, dy2: -1);
2477 break;
2478 }
2479 // As above, deal with the logical first, then convert it back to screen coords.
2480 QRect cr = visualRect(direction: btn->direction, boundingRect: btn->rect,
2481 logicalRect: subElementRect(sr: SE_CheckBoxContents, opt: btn, widget));
2482
2483 QRect iconRect, textRect;
2484 if (!btn->text.isEmpty()) {
2485 textRect = itemTextRect(fm: opt->fontMetrics, r: cr, flags: Qt::AlignAbsolute | Qt::AlignLeft
2486 | Qt::AlignVCenter | Qt::TextShowMnemonic,
2487 enabled: btn->state & State_Enabled, text: btn->text);
2488 }
2489 if (!btn->icon.isNull()) {
2490 iconRect = itemPixmapRect(r: cr, flags: Qt::AlignAbsolute | Qt::AlignLeft | Qt::AlignVCenter
2491 | Qt::TextShowMnemonic,
2492 pixmap: btn->icon.pixmap(size: btn->iconSize, devicePixelRatio: qt_getDevicePixelRatio(widget), mode: QIcon::Normal));
2493 if (!textRect.isEmpty())
2494 textRect.translate(dx: iconRect.right() + 4, dy: 0);
2495 }
2496 r = iconRect | textRect;
2497 r.adjust(dx1: -3, dy1: -2, dx2: 3, dy2: 2);
2498 r = r.intersected(other: btn->rect);
2499 r = visualRect(direction: btn->direction, boundingRect: btn->rect, logicalRect: r);
2500 }
2501 break;
2502
2503 case SE_RadioButtonIndicator:
2504 {
2505 int h = proxy()->pixelMetric(metric: PM_ExclusiveIndicatorHeight, option: opt, widget);
2506 r.setRect(ax: opt->rect.x(), ay: opt->rect.y() + ((opt->rect.height() - h) / 2),
2507 aw: proxy()->pixelMetric(metric: PM_ExclusiveIndicatorWidth, option: opt, widget), ah: h);
2508 r = visualRect(direction: opt->direction, boundingRect: opt->rect, logicalRect: r);
2509 }
2510 break;
2511
2512 case SE_RadioButtonContents:
2513 {
2514 QRect ir = visualRect(direction: opt->direction, boundingRect: opt->rect,
2515 logicalRect: subElementRect(sr: SE_RadioButtonIndicator, opt, widget));
2516 int spacing = proxy()->pixelMetric(metric: PM_RadioButtonLabelSpacing, option: opt, widget);
2517 r.setRect(ax: ir.left() + ir.width() + spacing, ay: opt->rect.y(), aw: opt->rect.width() - ir.width() - spacing,
2518 ah: opt->rect.height());
2519 r = visualRect(direction: opt->direction, boundingRect: opt->rect, logicalRect: r);
2520 break;
2521 }
2522
2523 case SE_RadioButtonFocusRect:
2524 if (const QStyleOptionButton *btn = qstyleoption_cast<const QStyleOptionButton *>(opt)) {
2525 if (btn->icon.isNull() && btn->text.isEmpty()) {
2526 r = subElementRect(sr: SE_RadioButtonIndicator, opt, widget);
2527 r.adjust(dx1: 1, dy1: 1, dx2: -1, dy2: -1);
2528 break;
2529 }
2530 QRect cr = visualRect(direction: btn->direction, boundingRect: btn->rect,
2531 logicalRect: subElementRect(sr: SE_RadioButtonContents, opt, widget));
2532
2533 QRect iconRect, textRect;
2534 if (!btn->text.isEmpty()){
2535 textRect = itemTextRect(fm: opt->fontMetrics, r: cr, flags: Qt::AlignAbsolute | Qt::AlignLeft | Qt::AlignVCenter
2536 | Qt::TextShowMnemonic, enabled: btn->state & State_Enabled, text: btn->text);

2827 case SE_TabBarTabLeftButton:
2828 case SE_TabBarTabRightButton:
2829 if (const QStyleOptionTab *tab = qstyleoption_cast<const QStyleOptionTab *>(opt)) {
2830 bool selected = tab->state & State_Selected;
2831 int verticalShift = proxy()->pixelMetric(metric: QStyle::PM_TabBarTabShiftVertical, option: tab, widget);
2832 int horizontalShift = proxy()->pixelMetric(metric: QStyle::PM_TabBarTabShiftHorizontal, option: tab, widget);
2833 int hpadding = proxy()->pixelMetric(metric: QStyle::PM_TabBarTabHSpace, option: opt, widget) / 2;
2834 hpadding = qMax(a: hpadding, b: 4); //workaround KStyle returning 0 because they workaround an old bug in Qt
2835
2836 bool verticalTabs = tab->shape == QTabBar::RoundedEast
2837 || tab->shape == QTabBar::RoundedWest
2838 || tab->shape == QTabBar::TriangularEast
2839 || tab->shape == QTabBar::TriangularWest;
2840
2841 QRect tr = tab->rect;
2842 if (tab->shape == QTabBar::RoundedSouth || tab->shape == QTabBar::TriangularSouth)
2843 verticalShift = -verticalShift;
2844 if (verticalTabs) {
2845 qSwap(value1&: horizontalShift, value2&: verticalShift);
2846 horizontalShift *= -1;
2847 verticalShift *= -1;
2848 }
2849 if (tab->shape == QTabBar::RoundedWest || tab->shape == QTabBar::TriangularWest)
2850 horizontalShift = -horizontalShift;
2851
2852 tr.adjust(dx1: 0, dy1: 0, dx2: horizontalShift, dy2: verticalShift);
2853 if (selected)
2854 {
2855 tr.setBottom(tr.bottom() - verticalShift);
2856 tr.setRight(tr.right() - horizontalShift);
2857 }

2859 QSize size = (sr == SE_TabBarTabLeftButton) ? tab->leftButtonSize : tab->rightButtonSize;
2860 int w = size.width();
2861 int h = size.height();
2862 int midHeight = static_cast<int>(qCeil(v: float(tr.height() - h) / 2));
2863 int midWidth = ((tr.width() - w) / 2);
2864
2865 bool atTheTop = true;
2866 switch (tab->shape) {
2867 case QTabBar::RoundedWest:
2868 case QTabBar::TriangularWest:
2869 atTheTop = (sr == SE_TabBarTabLeftButton);
2870 break;
2871 case QTabBar::RoundedEast:
2872 case QTabBar::TriangularEast:
2873 atTheTop = (sr == SE_TabBarTabRightButton);
2874 break;
2875 default:
2876 if (sr == SE_TabBarTabLeftButton)
2877 r = QRect(tab->rect.x() + hpadding, midHeight, w, h);
2878 else
2879 r = QRect(tab->rect.right() - w - hpadding, midHeight, w, h);
2880 r = visualRect(direction: tab->direction, boundingRect: tab->rect, logicalRect: r);
2881 }
2882 if (verticalTabs) {
2883 if (atTheTop)
2884 r = QRect(midWidth, tr.y() + tab->rect.height() - hpadding - h, w, h);
2885 else
2886 r = QRect(midWidth, tr.y() + hpadding, w, h);
2887 }
2888 }

2890 break;

2997 break;

3004#if QT_CONFIG(dockwidget)
3005 case SE_DockWidgetCloseButton:
3006 case SE_DockWidgetFloatButton:
3007 case SE_DockWidgetTitleBarText:
3008 case SE_DockWidgetIcon: {
3009 int iconSize = proxy()->pixelMetric(metric: PM_SmallIconSize, option: opt, widget);
3010 int buttonMargin = proxy()->pixelMetric(metric: PM_DockWidgetTitleBarButtonMargin, option: opt, widget);
3011 int margin = proxy()->pixelMetric(metric: QStyle::PM_DockWidgetTitleMargin, option: opt, widget);
3012 QRect rect = opt->rect;
3013
3014 const QStyleOptionDockWidget *dwOpt
3015 = qstyleoption_cast<const QStyleOptionDockWidget*>(opt);
3016 bool canClose = dwOpt == nullptr ? true : dwOpt->closable;
3017 bool canFloat = dwOpt == nullptr ? false : dwOpt->floatable;
3018
3019 const bool verticalTitleBar = dwOpt && dwOpt->verticalTitleBar;
3020
3021 // If this is a vertical titlebar, we transpose and work as if it was
3022 // horizontal, then transpose again.
3023
3024 if (verticalTitleBar)
3025 rect = rect.transposed();
3026
3027 do {
3028
3029 int right = rect.right();
3030 int left = rect.left();
3031
3032 QRect closeRect;
3033 if (canClose) {
3034 QSize sz = proxy()->standardIcon(standardIcon: QStyle::SP_TitleBarCloseButton,
3035 option: opt, widget).actualSize(size: QSize(iconSize, iconSize));
3036 sz += QSize(buttonMargin, buttonMargin);
3037 if (verticalTitleBar)
3038 sz = sz.transposed();
3039 closeRect = QRect(right - sz.width(),
3040 rect.center().y() - sz.height()/2,
3041 sz.width(), sz.height());
3042 right = closeRect.left() - 1;
3043 }
3044 if (sr == SE_DockWidgetCloseButton) {
3045 r = closeRect;
3046 break;
3047 }
3048
3049 QRect floatRect;
3050 if (canFloat) {
3051 QSize sz = proxy()->standardIcon(standardIcon: QStyle::SP_TitleBarNormalButton,
3052 option: opt, widget).actualSize(size: QSize(iconSize, iconSize));
3053 sz += QSize(buttonMargin, buttonMargin);
3054 if (verticalTitleBar)
3055 sz = sz.transposed();
3056 floatRect = QRect(right - sz.width(),
3057 rect.center().y() - sz.height()/2,
3058 sz.width(), sz.height());
3059 right = floatRect.left() - 1;
3060 }
3061 if (sr == SE_DockWidgetFloatButton) {
3062 r = floatRect;
3063 break;
3064 }
3065
3066 QRect iconRect;
3067 if (const QDockWidget *dw = qobject_cast<const QDockWidget*>(object: widget)) {
3068 QIcon icon;
3069 if (dw->isFloating())
3070 icon = dw->windowIcon();
3071 if (!icon.isNull()
3072 && icon.cacheKey() != QApplication::windowIcon().cacheKey()) {
3073 QSize sz = icon.actualSize(size: QSize(r.height(), r.height()));
3074 if (verticalTitleBar)
3075 sz = sz.transposed();
3076 iconRect = QRect(left, rect.center().y() - sz.height()/2,
3077 sz.width(), sz.height());
3078 left = iconRect.right() + margin;
3079 }
3080 }
3081 if (sr == SE_DockWidgetIcon) {
3082 r = iconRect;
3083 break;
3084 }
3085
3086 QRect textRect = QRect(left, rect.top(),
3087 right - left, rect.height());
3088 if (sr == SE_DockWidgetTitleBarText) {
3089 r = textRect;
3090 break;
3091 }
3092
3093 } while (false);
3094
3095 if (verticalTitleBar) {
3096 r = QRect(rect.left() + r.top() - rect.top(),
3097 rect.top() + rect.right() - r.right(),
3098 r.height(), r.width());
3099 } else {
3100 r = visualRect(direction: opt->direction, boundingRect: rect, logicalRect: r);
3101 }
3102 break;
3103 }
3104#endif
3105#if QT_CONFIG(itemviews)
3106 case SE_ItemViewItemCheckIndicator:
3107 if (!qstyleoption_cast<const QStyleOptionViewItem *>(opt)) {
3108 r = subElementRect(sr: SE_CheckBoxIndicator, opt, widget);
3109 break;
3110 }
3111 Q_FALLTHROUGH();
3112 case SE_ItemViewItemDecoration:
3113 case SE_ItemViewItemText:
3114 case SE_ItemViewItemFocusRect:
3115 if (const QStyleOptionViewItem *vopt = qstyleoption_cast<const QStyleOptionViewItem *>(opt)) {
3116 if (!d->isViewItemCached(option: *vopt)) {
3117 d->viewItemLayout(opt: vopt, checkRect: &d->checkRect, pixmapRect: &d->decorationRect, textRect: &d->displayRect, sizehint: false);
3118 if (d->cachedOption) {
3119 delete d->cachedOption;
3120 d->cachedOption = nullptr;
3121 }
3122 d->cachedOption = new QStyleOptionViewItem(*vopt);
3123 }
3124 if (sr == SE_ItemViewItemCheckIndicator)
3125 r = d->checkRect;
3126 else if (sr == SE_ItemViewItemDecoration)
3127 r = d->decorationRect;
3128 else if (sr == SE_ItemViewItemText || sr == SE_ItemViewItemFocusRect)
3129 r = d->displayRect;
3130 }
3131 break;
3132#endif // QT_CONFIG(itemviews)
3133#if QT_CONFIG(toolbar)
3134 case SE_ToolBarHandle:
3135 if (const QStyleOptionToolBar *tbopt = qstyleoption_cast<const QStyleOptionToolBar *>(opt)) {
3136 if (tbopt->features & QStyleOptionToolBar::Movable) {
3137 ///we need to access the widget here because the style option doesn't
3138 //have all the information we need (ie. the layout's margin)
3139 const QToolBar *tb = qobject_cast<const QToolBar*>(object: widget);
3140 const QMargins margins = tb && tb->layout() ? tb->layout()->contentsMargins() : QMargins(2, 2, 2, 2);
3141 const int handleExtent = proxy()->pixelMetric(metric: QStyle::PM_ToolBarHandleExtent, option: opt, widget: tb);
3142 if (tbopt->state & QStyle::State_Horizontal) {
3143 r = QRect(margins.left(), margins.top(),
3144 handleExtent,
3145 tbopt->rect.height() - (margins.top() + margins.bottom()));
3146 r = QStyle::visualRect(direction: tbopt->direction, boundingRect: tbopt->rect, logicalRect: r);
3147 } else {
3148 r = QRect(margins.left(), margins.top(),
3149 tbopt->rect.width() - (margins.left() + margins.right()),
3150 handleExtent);
3151 }
3152 }
3153 }
3154 break;
3155#endif // QT_CONFIG(toolbar)
3156 default:
3157 break;
3158 }
3159 return r;
3160#if !QT_CONFIG(tabwidget) && !QT_CONFIG(itemviews)
3161 Q_UNUSED(d);
3162#endif
3163}

3165#if QT_CONFIG(dial)
3166
3167// in lieu of std::array, minimal API
3168template <int N>
3169struct StaticPolygonF
3170{
3171 QPointF data[N];
3172
3173 constexpr int size() const { return N; }
3174 constexpr const QPointF *cbegin() const { return data; }
3175 constexpr const QPointF &operator[](int idx) const { return data[idx]; }
3176};
3177
3178static StaticPolygonF<3> calcArrow(const QStyleOptionSlider *dial, qreal &a)
3179{
3180 int width = dial->rect.width();
3181 int height = dial->rect.height();
3182 int r = qMin(a: width, b: height) / 2;
3183 int currentSliderPosition = dial->upsideDown ? dial->sliderPosition : (dial->maximum - dial->sliderPosition);
3184
3185 if (dial->maximum == dial->minimum)
3186 a = Q_PI / 2;
3187 else if (dial->dialWrapping)
3188 a = Q_PI * 3 / 2 - (currentSliderPosition - dial->minimum) * 2 * Q_PI
3189 / (dial->maximum - dial->minimum);
3190 else
3191 a = (Q_PI * 8 - (currentSliderPosition - dial->minimum) * 10 * Q_PI
3192 / (dial->maximum - dial->minimum)) / 6;
3193
3194 int xc = width / 2 + dial->rect.left();
3195 int yc = height / 2 + dial->rect.top();
3196
3197 int len = r - QStyleHelper::calcBigLineSize(radius: r) - 5;
3198 if (len < 5)
3199 len = 5;
3200 int back = len / 2;
3201
3202 StaticPolygonF<3> arrow = {.data: {
3203 QPointF(0.5 + xc + len * qCos(v: a),
3204 0.5 + yc - len * qSin(v: a)),
3205 QPointF(0.5 + xc + back * qCos(v: a + Q_PI * 5 / 6),
3206 0.5 + yc - back * qSin(v: a + Q_PI * 5 / 6)),
3207 QPointF(0.5 + xc + back * qCos(v: a - Q_PI * 5 / 6),
3208 0.5 + yc - back * qSin(v: a - Q_PI * 5 / 6)),
3209 }};
3210 return arrow;
3211}
3212
3213#endif // QT_CONFIG(dial)

3215/*!
3216 \reimp
3217*/
3218void QCommonStyle::drawComplexControl(ComplexControl cc, const QStyleOptionComplex *opt,
3219 QPainter *p, const QWidget *widget) const
3220{
3221 switch (cc) {
3222#if QT_CONFIG(slider)
3223 case CC_Slider:
3224 if (const QStyleOptionSlider *slider = qstyleoption_cast<const QStyleOptionSlider *>(opt)) {
3225 if (slider->subControls == SC_SliderTickmarks) {
3226 int tickOffset = proxy()->pixelMetric(metric: PM_SliderTickmarkOffset, option: slider, widget);
3227 int ticks = slider->tickPosition;
3228 int thickness = proxy()->pixelMetric(metric: PM_SliderControlThickness, option: slider, widget);
3229 int len = proxy()->pixelMetric(metric: PM_SliderLength, option: slider, widget);
3230 int available = proxy()->pixelMetric(metric: PM_SliderSpaceAvailable, option: slider, widget);
3231 int interval = slider->tickInterval;
3232 if (interval <= 0) {
3233 interval = slider->singleStep;
3234 if (QStyle::sliderPositionFromValue(min: slider->minimum, max: slider->maximum, val: interval,
3235 space: available)
3236 - QStyle::sliderPositionFromValue(min: slider->minimum, max: slider->maximum,
3237 val: 0, space: available) < 3)
3238 interval = slider->pageStep;
3239 }
3240 if (!interval)
3241 interval = 1;
3242 int fudge = len / 2;
3243 int pos;
3244 // Since there is no subrect for tickmarks do a translation here.
3245 p->save();
3246 p->translate(dx: slider->rect.x(), dy: slider->rect.y());
3247 p->setPen(slider->palette.windowText().color());
3248 int v = slider->minimum;
3249 while (v <= slider->maximum + 1) {
3250 if (v == slider->maximum + 1 && interval == 1)
3251 break;
3252 const int v_ = qMin(a: v, b: slider->maximum);
3253 pos = QStyle::sliderPositionFromValue(min: slider->minimum, max: slider->maximum,
3254 val: v_, space: available) + fudge;
3255 if (slider->orientation == Qt::Horizontal) {
3256 if (ticks & QSlider::TicksAbove)
3257 p->drawLine(x1: pos, y1: 0, x2: pos, y2: tickOffset - 2);
3258 if (ticks & QSlider::TicksBelow)
3259 p->drawLine(x1: pos, y1: tickOffset + thickness + 1, x2: pos,
3260 y2: slider->rect.height()-1);
3261 } else {
3262 if (ticks & QSlider::TicksAbove)
3263 p->drawLine(x1: 0, y1: pos, x2: tickOffset - 2, y2: pos);
3264 if (ticks & QSlider::TicksBelow)
3265 p->drawLine(x1: tickOffset + thickness + 1, y1: pos,
3266 x2: slider->rect.width()-1, y2: pos);
3267 }
3268 // in the case where maximum is max int
3269 int nextInterval = v + interval;
3270 if (nextInterval < v)
3271 break;
3272 v = nextInterval;
3273 }
3274 p->restore();
3275 }
3276 }
3277 break;
3278#endif // QT_CONFIG(slider)
3279#if QT_CONFIG(scrollbar)

3518 flags: Qt::AlignLeft | Qt::AlignVCenter | Qt::TextSingleLine, str: tb->text);

3702 p->setBrush(Qt::NoBrush);

3717 p->setBrush(Qt::NoBrush);

3729 p->drawLine(p1: arrow[1], p2: arrow[2]);
3730 p->drawLine(p1: arrow[0], p2: arrow[1]);

3733 p->drawLine(p1: arrow[2], p2: arrow[0]);
3734 p->drawLine(p1: arrow[1], p2: arrow[2]);
3735 p->setPen(pal.light().color());
3736 p->drawLine(p1: arrow[0], p2: arrow[1]);
3737 } else if (a >= 135 && a < 200) {
3738 p->setPen(pal.dark().color());
3739 p->drawLine(p1: arrow[2], p2: arrow[0]);
3740 p->setPen(pal.light().color());
3741 p->drawLine(p1: arrow[0], p2: arrow[1]);

3752 if (dial->subControls & SC_DialTickmarks) {
3753 int r = qMin(a: width, b: height) / 2;
3754 br.translate(dx: -r / 6, dy: - r / 6);
3755 br.setWidth(br.width() + r / 3);
3756 br.setHeight(br.height() + r / 3);
3757 }
3758 fropt.rect = br.adjusted(xp1: -2, yp1: -2, xp2: 2, yp2: 2);
3759 proxy()->drawPrimitive(pe: QStyle::PE_FrameFocusRect, opt: &fropt, p, w: widget);
3760 }
3761 p->restore();

3765#if QT_CONFIG(groupbox)
