3895
3896/*!
3897 \reimp
3898*/
3899QStyle::SubControl QCommonStyle::hitTestComplexControl(ComplexControl cc, const QStyleOptionComplex *opt,
3900 const QPoint &pt, const QWidget *widget) const
3901{
3902 SubControl sc = SC_None;
3903 switch (cc) {
3904#if QT_CONFIG(slider)
3905 case CC_Slider:
3906 if (const QStyleOptionSlider *slider = qstyleoption_cast<const QStyleOptionSlider *>(opt)) {
3907 QRect r = proxy()->subControlRect(cc, opt: slider, sc: SC_SliderHandle, widget);
3908 if (r.isValid() && r.contains(p: pt)) {
3909 sc = SC_SliderHandle;
3910 } else {
3911 r = proxy()->subControlRect(cc, opt: slider, sc: SC_SliderGroove ,widget);
3912 if (r.isValid() && r.contains(p: pt))
3913 sc = SC_SliderGroove;
3914 }
3915 }
3916 break;
3917#endif // QT_CONFIG(slider)
3918#if QT_CONFIG(scrollbar)
3919 case CC_ScrollBar:
3920 if (const QStyleOptionSlider *scrollbar = qstyleoption_cast<const QStyleOptionSlider *>(opt)) {
3921 QRect r;
3922 uint ctrl = SC_ScrollBarAddLine;
3923 while (ctrl <= SC_ScrollBarGroove) {
3924 r = proxy()->subControlRect(cc, opt: scrollbar, sc: QStyle::SubControl(ctrl), widget);
3925 if (r.isValid() && r.contains(p: pt)) {
3926 sc = QStyle::SubControl(ctrl);
3927 break;
3928 }
3929 ctrl <<= 1;
3930 }
3931 }
3932 break;
3933#endif // QT_CONFIG(scrollbar)
3934#if QT_CONFIG(toolbutton)
3935 case CC_ToolButton:
3936 if (const QStyleOptionToolButton *toolbutton = qstyleoption_cast<const QStyleOptionToolButton *>(opt)) {
3937 QRect r;
3938 uint ctrl = SC_ToolButton;
3939 while (ctrl <= SC_ToolButtonMenu) {
3940 r = proxy()->subControlRect(cc, opt: toolbutton, sc: QStyle::SubControl(ctrl), widget);
3941 if (r.isValid() && r.contains(p: pt)) {
3942 sc = QStyle::SubControl(ctrl);
3943 break;
3944 }
3945 ctrl <<= 1;
3946 }
3947 }
3948 break;
3949#endif // QT_CONFIG(toolbutton)
3950#if QT_CONFIG(spinbox)
3951 case CC_SpinBox:
3952 if (const QStyleOptionSpinBox *spinbox = qstyleoption_cast<const QStyleOptionSpinBox *>(opt)) {
3953 QRect r;
3954 uint ctrl = SC_SpinBoxUp;
3955 while (ctrl <= SC_SpinBoxEditField) {
3956 r = proxy()->subControlRect(cc, opt: spinbox, sc: QStyle::SubControl(ctrl), widget);
3957 if (r.isValid() && r.contains(p: pt)) {
3958 sc = QStyle::SubControl(ctrl);
3959 break;
3960 }
3961 ctrl <<= 1;
3962 }
3963 }
3964 break;
3965#endif // QT_CONFIG(spinbox)
3966 case CC_TitleBar:
3967 if (const QStyleOptionTitleBar *tb = qstyleoption_cast<const QStyleOptionTitleBar *>(opt)) {
3968 QRect r;
3969 uint ctrl = SC_TitleBarSysMenu;
3970
3971 while (ctrl <= SC_TitleBarLabel) {
3972 r = proxy()->subControlRect(cc, opt: tb, sc: QStyle::SubControl(ctrl), widget);
3973 if (r.isValid() && r.contains(p: pt)) {
3974 sc = QStyle::SubControl(ctrl);
3975 break;
3976 }
3977 ctrl <<= 1;
3978 }
3979 }
3980 break;
3981#if QT_CONFIG(combobox)
3982 case CC_ComboBox:
3983 if (const QStyleOptionComboBox *cb = qstyleoption_cast<const QStyleOptionComboBox *>(opt)) {
3984 QRect r;
3985 uint ctrl = SC_ComboBoxArrow; // Start here and go down.
3986 while (ctrl > 0) {
3987 r = proxy()->subControlRect(cc, opt: cb, sc: QStyle::SubControl(ctrl), widget);
3988 if (r.isValid() && r.contains(p: pt)) {
3989 sc = QStyle::SubControl(ctrl);
3990 break;
3991 }
3992 ctrl >>= 1;
3993 }
3994 }
3995 break;
3996#endif // QT_CONFIG(combobox)
3997#if QT_CONFIG(groupbox)
3998 case CC_GroupBox:
3999 if (const QStyleOptionGroupBox *groupBox = qstyleoption_cast<const QStyleOptionGroupBox *>(opt)) {
4000 QRect r;
4001 uint ctrl = SC_GroupBoxCheckBox;
4002 while (ctrl <= SC_GroupBoxFrame) {
4003 r = proxy()->subControlRect(cc, opt: groupBox, sc: QStyle::SubControl(ctrl), widget);
4004 if (r.isValid() && r.contains(p: pt)) {
4005 sc = QStyle::SubControl(ctrl);
4006 break;
4007 }
4008 ctrl <<= 1;
4009 }
4010 }
4011 break;
4012#endif // QT_CONFIG(groupbox)
4013 case CC_MdiControls:
4014 {
4015 QRect r;
4016 uint ctrl = SC_MdiMinButton;
4017 while (ctrl <= SC_MdiCloseButton) {
4018 r = proxy()->subControlRect(cc: CC_MdiControls, opt, sc: QStyle::SubControl(ctrl), widget);
4019 if (r.isValid() && r.contains(p: pt) && (opt->subControls & ctrl)) {
4020 sc = QStyle::SubControl(ctrl);
4021 return sc;
4022 }
4023 ctrl <<= 1;
4024 }
4025 }
4026 break;
4027 default:
4028 qCWarning(lcCommonStyle, "QCommonStyle::hitTestComplexControl: Case %d not handled", cc);
4029 }
4030 return sc;
4031}
4032
4033/*!
4034 \reimp
4035*/
4036QRect QCommonStyle::subControlRect(ComplexControl cc, const QStyleOptionComplex *opt,
4037 SubControl sc, const QWidget *widget) const
4038{
4039 QRect ret;
4040 switch (cc) {
4041#if QT_CONFIG(slider)
4042 case CC_Slider:
4043 if (const QStyleOptionSlider *slider = qstyleoption_cast<const QStyleOptionSlider *>(opt)) {
4044 int tickOffset = proxy()->pixelMetric(metric: PM_SliderTickmarkOffset, option: slider, widget);
4045 int thickness = proxy()->pixelMetric(metric: PM_SliderControlThickness, option: slider, widget);
4046
4047 switch (sc) {
4048 case SC_SliderHandle: {
4049 int sliderPos = 0;
4050 int len = proxy()->pixelMetric(metric: PM_SliderLength, option: slider, widget);
4051 bool horizontal = slider->orientation == Qt::Horizontal;
4052 sliderPos = sliderPositionFromValue(min: slider->minimum, max: slider->maximum,
4053 val: slider->sliderPosition,
4054 space: (horizontal ? slider->rect.width()
4055 : slider->rect.height()) - len,
4056 upsideDown: slider->upsideDown);
4057 if (horizontal)
4058 ret.setRect(ax: slider->rect.x() + sliderPos, ay: slider->rect.y() + tickOffset, aw: len, ah: thickness);
4059 else
4060 ret.setRect(ax: slider->rect.x() + tickOffset, ay: slider->rect.y() + sliderPos, aw: thickness, ah: len);
4061 break; }
4062 case SC_SliderGroove:
4063 if (slider->orientation == Qt::Horizontal)
4064 ret.setRect(ax: slider->rect.x(), ay: slider->rect.y() + tickOffset,
4065 aw: slider->rect.width(), ah: thickness);
4066 else
4067 ret.setRect(ax: slider->rect.x() + tickOffset, ay: slider->rect.y(),
4068 aw: thickness, ah: slider->rect.height());
4069 break;
4070 default:
4071 break;
4072 }
4073 ret = visualRect(direction: slider->direction, boundingRect: slider->rect, logicalRect: ret);
4074 }
4075 break;
4076#endif // QT_CONFIG(slider)
4077#if QT_CONFIG(scrollbar)
4078 case CC_ScrollBar:
4079 if (const QStyleOptionSlider *scrollbar = qstyleoption_cast<const QStyleOptionSlider *>(opt)) {
4080 const QRect scrollBarRect = scrollbar->rect;
4081 int sbextent = 0;
4082 if (!proxy()->styleHint(stylehint: SH_ScrollBar_Transient, opt: scrollbar, widget))
4083 sbextent = proxy()->pixelMetric(metric: PM_ScrollBarExtent, option: scrollbar, widget);
4084 int maxlen = ((scrollbar->orientation == Qt::Horizontal) ?
4085 scrollBarRect.width() : scrollBarRect.height()) - (sbextent * 2);
4086 int sliderlen;
4087
4088 // calculate slider length
4089 if (scrollbar->maximum != scrollbar->minimum) {
4090 uint range = scrollbar->maximum - scrollbar->minimum;
4091 sliderlen = (qint64(scrollbar->pageStep) * maxlen) / (range + scrollbar->pageStep);
4092
4093 int slidermin = proxy()->pixelMetric(metric: PM_ScrollBarSliderMin, option: scrollbar, widget);
4094 if (sliderlen < slidermin || range > INT_MAX / 2)
4095 sliderlen = slidermin;
4096 if (sliderlen > maxlen)
4097 sliderlen = maxlen;
4098 } else {
4099 sliderlen = maxlen;
4100 }
4101
4102 int sliderstart = sbextent + sliderPositionFromValue(min: scrollbar->minimum,
4103 max: scrollbar->maximum,
4104 val: scrollbar->sliderPosition,
4105 space: maxlen - sliderlen,
4106 upsideDown: scrollbar->upsideDown);
4107
4108 switch (sc) {
4109 case SC_ScrollBarSubLine: // top/left button
4110 if (scrollbar->orientation == Qt::Horizontal) {
4111 int buttonWidth = qMin(a: scrollBarRect.width() / 2, b: sbextent);
4112 ret.setRect(ax: 0, ay: 0, aw: buttonWidth, ah: scrollBarRect.height());
4113 } else {
4114 int buttonHeight = qMin(a: scrollBarRect.height() / 2, b: sbextent);
4115 ret.setRect(ax: 0, ay: 0, aw: scrollBarRect.width(), ah: buttonHeight);
4116 }
4117 break;
4118 case SC_ScrollBarAddLine: // bottom/right button
4119 if (scrollbar->orientation == Qt::Horizontal) {
4120 int buttonWidth = qMin(a: scrollBarRect.width()/2, b: sbextent);
4121 ret.setRect(ax: scrollBarRect.width() - buttonWidth, ay: 0, aw: buttonWidth, ah: scrollBarRect.height());
4122 } else {
4123 int buttonHeight = qMin(a: scrollBarRect.height()/2, b: sbextent);
4124 ret.setRect(ax: 0, ay: scrollBarRect.height() - buttonHeight, aw: scrollBarRect.width(), ah: buttonHeight);
4125 }
4126 break;
4127 case SC_ScrollBarSubPage: // between top/left button and slider
4128 if (scrollbar->orientation == Qt::Horizontal)
4129 ret.setRect(ax: sbextent, ay: 0, aw: sliderstart - sbextent, ah: scrollBarRect.height());
4130 else
4131 ret.setRect(ax: 0, ay: sbextent, aw: scrollBarRect.width(), ah: sliderstart - sbextent);
4132 break;
4133 case SC_ScrollBarAddPage: // between bottom/right button and slider
4134 if (scrollbar->orientation == Qt::Horizontal)
4135 ret.setRect(ax: sliderstart + sliderlen, ay: 0,
4136 aw: maxlen - sliderstart - sliderlen + sbextent, ah: scrollBarRect.height());
4137 else
4138 ret.setRect(ax: 0, ay: sliderstart + sliderlen, aw: scrollBarRect.width(),
4139 ah: maxlen - sliderstart - sliderlen + sbextent);
4140 break;
4141 case SC_ScrollBarGroove:
4142 if (scrollbar->orientation == Qt::Horizontal)
4143 ret.setRect(ax: sbextent, ay: 0, aw: scrollBarRect.width() - sbextent * 2,
4144 ah: scrollBarRect.height());
4145 else
4146 ret.setRect(ax: 0, ay: sbextent, aw: scrollBarRect.width(),
4147 ah: scrollBarRect.height() - sbextent * 2);
4148 break;
4149 case SC_ScrollBarSlider:
4150 if (scrollbar->orientation == Qt::Horizontal)
4151 ret.setRect(ax: sliderstart, ay: 0, aw: sliderlen, ah: scrollBarRect.height());
4152 else
4153 ret.setRect(ax: 0, ay: sliderstart, aw: scrollBarRect.width(), ah: sliderlen);
4154 break;
4155 default:
4156 break;
4157 }
4158 ret = visualRect(direction: scrollbar->direction, boundingRect: scrollBarRect, logicalRect: ret);
4159 }
4160 break;
4161#endif // QT_CONFIG(scrollbar)
4162#if QT_CONFIG(spinbox)
4163 case CC_SpinBox:
4164 if (const QStyleOptionSpinBox *spinbox = qstyleoption_cast<const QStyleOptionSpinBox *>(opt)) {
4165 QSize bs;
4166 int fw = spinbox->frame ? proxy()->pixelMetric(metric: PM_SpinBoxFrameWidth, option: spinbox, widget) : 0;
4167 bs.setHeight(qMax(a: 8, b: spinbox->rect.height()/2 - fw));
4168 // 1.6 -approximate golden mean
4169 bs.setWidth(qMax(a: 16, b: qMin(a: bs.height() * 8 / 5, b: spinbox->rect.width() / 4)));
4170 int y = fw + spinbox->rect.y();
4171 int x, lx, rx;
4172 x = spinbox->rect.x() + spinbox->rect.width() - fw - bs.width();
4173 lx = fw;
4174 rx = x - fw;
4175 switch (sc) {
4176 case SC_SpinBoxUp:
4177 if (spinbox->buttonSymbols == QAbstractSpinBox::NoButtons)
4178 return QRect();
4179 ret = QRect(x, y, bs.width(), bs.height());
4180 break;
4181 case SC_SpinBoxDown:
4182 if (spinbox->buttonSymbols == QAbstractSpinBox::NoButtons)
4183 return QRect();
4184
4185 ret = QRect(x, y + bs.height(), bs.width(), bs.height());
4186 break;
4187 case SC_SpinBoxEditField:
4188 if (spinbox->buttonSymbols == QAbstractSpinBox::NoButtons) {
4189 ret = QRect(lx, fw, spinbox->rect.width() - 2*fw, spinbox->rect.height() - 2*fw);
4190 } else {
4191 ret = QRect(lx, fw, rx, spinbox->rect.height() - 2*fw);
4192 }
4193 break;
4194 case SC_SpinBoxFrame:
4195 ret = spinbox->rect;
4196 default:
4197 break;
4198 }
4199 ret = visualRect(direction: spinbox->direction, boundingRect: spinbox->rect, logicalRect: ret);
4200 }
4201 break;
4202#endif // Qt_NO_SPINBOX
4203#if QT_CONFIG(toolbutton)
4204 case CC_ToolButton:
4205 if (const QStyleOptionToolButton *tb = qstyleoption_cast<const QStyleOptionToolButton *>(opt)) {
4206 int mbi = proxy()->pixelMetric(metric: PM_MenuButtonIndicator, option: tb, widget);
4207 ret = tb->rect;
4208 switch (sc) {
4209 case SC_ToolButton:
4210 if ((tb->features
4211 & (QStyleOptionToolButton::MenuButtonPopup | QStyleOptionToolButton::PopupDelay))
4212 == QStyleOptionToolButton::MenuButtonPopup)
4213 ret.adjust(dx1: 0, dy1: 0, dx2: -mbi, dy2: 0);
4214 break;
4215 case SC_ToolButtonMenu:
4216 if ((tb->features
4217 & (QStyleOptionToolButton::MenuButtonPopup | QStyleOptionToolButton::PopupDelay))
4218 == QStyleOptionToolButton::MenuButtonPopup)
4219 ret.adjust(dx1: ret.width() - mbi, dy1: 0, dx2: 0, dy2: 0);
4220 break;
4221 default:
4222 break;
4223 }
4224 ret = visualRect(direction: tb->direction, boundingRect: tb->rect, logicalRect: ret);
4225 }
4226 break;
4227#endif // QT_CONFIG(toolbutton)
4228#if QT_CONFIG(combobox)
4229 case CC_ComboBox:
4230 if (const QStyleOptionComboBox *cb = qstyleoption_cast<const QStyleOptionComboBox *>(opt)) {
4231 const qreal dpi = QStyleHelper::dpi(option: opt);
4232 const int x = cb->rect.x(), y = cb->rect.y(), wi = cb->rect.width(), he = cb->rect.height();
4233 const int margin = cb->frame ? qRound(d: QStyleHelper::dpiScaled(value: 3, dpi)) : 0;
4234 const int bmarg = cb->frame ? qRound(d: QStyleHelper::dpiScaled(value: 2, dpi)) : 0;
4235 const int xpos = x + wi - bmarg - qRound(d: QStyleHelper::dpiScaled(value: 16, dpi));
4236
4237
4238 switch (sc) {
4239 case SC_ComboBoxFrame:
4240 ret = cb->rect;
4241 break;
4242 case SC_ComboBoxArrow:
4243 ret.setRect(ax: xpos, ay: y + bmarg, aw: qRound(d: QStyleHelper::dpiScaled(value: 16, option: opt)), ah: he - 2*bmarg);
4244 break;
4245 case SC_ComboBoxEditField:
4246 ret.setRect(ax: x + margin, ay: y + margin, aw: wi - 2 * margin - qRound(d: QStyleHelper::dpiScaled(value: 16, dpi)), ah: he - 2 * margin);
4247 break;
4248 case SC_ComboBoxListBoxPopup:
4249 ret = cb->rect;
4250 break;
4251 default:
4252 break;
4253 }
4254 ret = visualRect(direction: cb->direction, boundingRect: cb->rect, logicalRect: ret);
4255 }
4256 break;
4257#endif // QT_CONFIG(combobox)
4258 case CC_TitleBar:
4259 if (const QStyleOptionTitleBar *tb = qstyleoption_cast<const QStyleOptionTitleBar *>(opt)) {
4260 const int controlMargin = 2;
4261 const int controlHeight = tb->rect.height() - controlMargin *2;
4262 const int delta = controlHeight + controlMargin;
4263 int offset = 0;
4264
4265 bool isMinimized = tb->titleBarState & Qt::WindowMinimized;
4266 bool isMaximized = tb->titleBarState & Qt::WindowMaximized;
4267
4268 switch (sc) {
4269 case SC_TitleBarLabel:
4270 if (tb->titleBarFlags & (Qt::WindowTitleHint | Qt::WindowSystemMenuHint)) {
4271 ret = tb->rect;
4272 if (tb->titleBarFlags & Qt::WindowSystemMenuHint)
4273 ret.adjust(dx1: delta, dy1: 0, dx2: -delta, dy2: 0);
4274 if (tb->titleBarFlags & Qt::WindowMinimizeButtonHint)
4275 ret.adjust(dx1: 0, dy1: 0, dx2: -delta, dy2: 0);
4276 if (tb->titleBarFlags & Qt::WindowMaximizeButtonHint)
4277 ret.adjust(dx1: 0, dy1: 0, dx2: -delta, dy2: 0);
4278 if (tb->titleBarFlags & Qt::WindowShadeButtonHint)
4279 ret.adjust(dx1: 0, dy1: 0, dx2: -delta, dy2: 0);
4280 if (tb->titleBarFlags & Qt::WindowContextHelpButtonHint)
4281 ret.adjust(dx1: 0, dy1: 0, dx2: -delta, dy2: 0);
4282 }
4283 break;
4284 case SC_TitleBarContextHelpButton:
4285 if (tb->titleBarFlags & Qt::WindowContextHelpButtonHint)
4286 offset += delta;
4287 Q_FALLTHROUGH();
4288 case SC_TitleBarMinButton:
4289 if (!isMinimized && (tb->titleBarFlags & Qt::WindowMinimizeButtonHint))
4290 offset += delta;
4291 else if (sc == SC_TitleBarMinButton)
4292 break;
4293 Q_FALLTHROUGH();
4294 case SC_TitleBarNormalButton:
4295 if (isMinimized && (tb->titleBarFlags & Qt::WindowMinimizeButtonHint))
4296 offset += delta;
4297 else if (isMaximized && (tb->titleBarFlags & Qt::WindowMaximizeButtonHint))
4298 offset += delta;
4299 else if (sc == SC_TitleBarNormalButton)
4300 break;
4301 Q_FALLTHROUGH();
4302 case SC_TitleBarMaxButton:
4303 if (!isMaximized && (tb->titleBarFlags & Qt::WindowMaximizeButtonHint))
4304 offset += delta;
4305 else if (sc == SC_TitleBarMaxButton)
4306 break;
4307 Q_FALLTHROUGH();
4308 case SC_TitleBarShadeButton:
4309 if (!isMinimized && (tb->titleBarFlags & Qt::WindowShadeButtonHint))
4310 offset += delta;
4311 else if (sc == SC_TitleBarShadeButton)
4312 break;
4313 Q_FALLTHROUGH();
4314 case SC_TitleBarUnshadeButton:
4315 if (isMinimized && (tb->titleBarFlags & Qt::WindowShadeButtonHint))
4316 offset += delta;
4317 else if (sc == SC_TitleBarUnshadeButton)
4318 break;
4319 Q_FALLTHROUGH();
4320 case SC_TitleBarCloseButton:
4321 if (tb->titleBarFlags & Qt::WindowSystemMenuHint)
4322 offset += delta;
4323 else if (sc == SC_TitleBarCloseButton)
4324 break;
4325 ret.setRect(ax: tb->rect.right() - offset, ay: tb->rect.top() + controlMargin,
4326 aw: controlHeight, ah: controlHeight);
4327 break;
4328 case SC_TitleBarSysMenu:
4329 if (tb->titleBarFlags & Qt::WindowSystemMenuHint) {
4330 ret.setRect(ax: tb->rect.left() + controlMargin, ay: tb->rect.top() + controlMargin,
4331 aw: controlHeight, ah: controlHeight);
4332 }
4333 break;
4334 default:
4335 break;
4336 }
4337 ret = visualRect(direction: tb->direction, boundingRect: tb->rect, logicalRect: ret);
4338 }
4339 break;
4340#if QT_CONFIG(groupbox)
4341 case CC_GroupBox: {
4342 if (const QStyleOptionGroupBox *groupBox = qstyleoption_cast<const QStyleOptionGroupBox *>(opt)) {
4343 switch (sc) {
4344 case SC_GroupBoxFrame:
4345 case SC_GroupBoxContents: {
4346 int topMargin = 0;
4347 int topHeight = 0;
4348 int verticalAlignment = proxy()->styleHint(stylehint: SH_GroupBox_TextLabelVerticalAlignment, opt: groupBox, widget);
4349 bool hasCheckBox = groupBox->subControls & QStyle::SC_GroupBoxCheckBox;
4350 if (groupBox->text.size() || hasCheckBox) {
4351 int checkBoxHeight = hasCheckBox ? proxy()->pixelMetric(metric: PM_IndicatorHeight, option: groupBox, widget) : 0;
4352 topHeight = qMax(a: groupBox->fontMetrics.height(), b: checkBoxHeight);
4353 if (verticalAlignment & Qt::AlignVCenter)
4354 topMargin = topHeight / 2;
4355 else if (verticalAlignment & Qt::AlignTop)
4356 topMargin = topHeight;
4357 }
4358
4359 QRect frameRect = groupBox->rect;
4360 frameRect.setTop(topMargin);
4361
4362 if (sc == SC_GroupBoxFrame) {
4363 ret = frameRect;
4364 break;
4365 }
4366
4367 int frameWidth = 0;
4368 if ((groupBox->features & QStyleOptionFrame::Flat) == 0)
4369 frameWidth = proxy()->pixelMetric(metric: PM_DefaultFrameWidth, option: groupBox, widget);
4370 ret = frameRect.adjusted(xp1: frameWidth, yp1: frameWidth + topHeight - topMargin,
4371 xp2: -frameWidth, yp2: -frameWidth);
4372 break;
4373 }
4374 case SC_GroupBoxCheckBox:
4375 case SC_GroupBoxLabel: {
4376 QFontMetrics fontMetrics = groupBox->fontMetrics;
4377 int th = fontMetrics.height();
4378 int tw = fontMetrics.size(flags: Qt::TextShowMnemonic, str: groupBox->text + u' ').width();
4379 int marg = (groupBox->features & QStyleOptionFrame::Flat) ? 0 : 8;
4380 ret = groupBox->rect.adjusted(xp1: marg, yp1: 0, xp2: -marg, yp2: 0);
4381
4382 int indicatorWidth = proxy()->pixelMetric(metric: PM_IndicatorWidth, option: opt, widget);
4383 int indicatorHeight = proxy()->pixelMetric(metric: PM_IndicatorHeight, option: opt, widget);
4384 int indicatorSpace = proxy()->pixelMetric(metric: PM_CheckBoxLabelSpacing, option: opt, widget) - 1;
4385 bool hasCheckBox = groupBox->subControls & QStyle::SC_GroupBoxCheckBox;
4386 int checkBoxWidth = hasCheckBox ? (indicatorWidth + indicatorSpace) : 0;
4387 int checkBoxHeight = hasCheckBox ? indicatorHeight : 0;
4388
4389 int h = qMax(a: th, b: checkBoxHeight);
4390 ret.setHeight(h);
4391
4392 // Adjusted rect for label + indicatorWidth + indicatorSpace
4393 QRect totalRect = alignedRect(direction: groupBox->direction, alignment: groupBox->textAlignment,
4394 size: QSize(tw + checkBoxWidth, h), rectangle: ret);
4395
4396 // Adjust totalRect if checkbox is set
4397 if (hasCheckBox) {
4398 bool ltr = groupBox->direction == Qt::LeftToRight;
4399 int left = 0;
4400 // Adjust for check box
4401 if (sc == SC_GroupBoxCheckBox) {
4402 left = ltr ? totalRect.left() : (totalRect.right() - indicatorWidth);
4403 int top = totalRect.top() + (h - checkBoxHeight) / 2;
4404 totalRect.setRect(ax: left, ay: top, aw: indicatorWidth, ah: indicatorHeight);
4405 // Adjust for label
4406 } else {
4407 left = ltr ? (totalRect.left() + checkBoxWidth - 2) : totalRect.left();
4408 int top = totalRect.top() + (h - th) / 2;
4409 totalRect.setRect(ax: left, ay: top, aw: totalRect.width() - checkBoxWidth, ah: th);
4410 }
4411 }
4412 ret = totalRect;
4413 break;
4414 }
4415 default:
4416 break;
4417 }
4418 }
4419 break;
4420 }
4421#endif // QT_CONFIG(groupbox)
4422#if QT_CONFIG(mdiarea)
4423 case CC_MdiControls:
4424 {
4425 int numSubControls = 0;
4426 if (opt->subControls & SC_MdiCloseButton)
4427 ++numSubControls;
4428 if (opt->subControls & SC_MdiMinButton)
4429 ++numSubControls;
4430 if (opt->subControls & SC_MdiNormalButton)
4431 ++numSubControls;
4432 if (numSubControls == 0)
4433 break;
4434
4435 int buttonWidth = opt->rect.width() / numSubControls - 1;
4436 int offset = 0;
4437 switch (sc) {
4438 case SC_MdiCloseButton:
4439 // Only one sub control, no offset needed.
4440 if (numSubControls == 1)
4441 break;
4442 offset += buttonWidth + 2;
4443 Q_FALLTHROUGH();
4444 case SC_MdiNormalButton:
4445 // No offset needed if
4446 // 1) There's only one sub control
4447 // 2) We have a close button and a normal button (offset already added in SC_MdiClose)
4448 if (numSubControls == 1 || (numSubControls == 2 && !(opt->subControls & SC_MdiMinButton)))
4449 break;
4450 if (opt->subControls & SC_MdiNormalButton)
4451 offset += buttonWidth;
4452 break;
4453 default:
4454 break;
4455 }
4456
4457 // Subtract one pixel if we only have one sub control. At this point
4458 // buttonWidth is the actual width + 1 pixel margin, but we don't want the
4459 // margin when there are no other controllers.
4460 if (numSubControls == 1)
4461 --buttonWidth;
4462 ret = QRect(offset, 0, buttonWidth, opt->rect.height());
4463 break;
4464 }
4465#endif // QT_CONFIG(mdiarea)
4466 default:
4467 qCWarning(lcCommonStyle, "QCommonStyle::subControlRect: Case %d not handled", cc);
4468 }
4469#if !QT_CONFIG(slider) && !QT_CONFIG(spinbox) && !QT_CONFIG(toolbutton) && !QT_CONFIG(groupbox)
4470 Q_UNUSED(widget);
4471#endif
4472 return ret;
4473}
4474
4475/*! \reimp */
4476int QCommonStyle::pixelMetric(PixelMetric m, const QStyleOption *opt, const QWidget *widget) const
4477{
4478 int ret;
4479
4480 switch (m) {
4481 case PM_FocusFrameVMargin:
4482 case PM_FocusFrameHMargin:
4483 ret = 2;
4484 break;
4485 case PM_MenuBarVMargin:
4486 case PM_MenuBarHMargin:
4487 ret = 0;
4488 break;
4489 case PM_DialogButtonsSeparator:
4490 ret = int(QStyleHelper::dpiScaled(value: 5, option: opt));
4491 break;
4492 case PM_DialogButtonsButtonWidth:
4493 ret = int(QStyleHelper::dpiScaled(value: 70, option: opt));
4494 break;
4495 case PM_DialogButtonsButtonHeight:
4496 ret = int(QStyleHelper::dpiScaled(value: 30, option: opt));
4497 break;
4498 case PM_TitleBarHeight:
4499 {
4500 if (const QStyleOptionTitleBar *tb = qstyleoption_cast<const QStyleOptionTitleBar *>(opt)) {
4501 if ((tb->titleBarFlags & Qt::WindowType_Mask) == Qt::Tool) {
4502 ret = qMax(a: widget ? widget->fontMetrics().height() : opt->fontMetrics.height(), b: 16);
4503#if QT_CONFIG(dockwidget)
4504 } else if (qobject_cast<const QDockWidget*>(object: widget)) {
4505 ret = qMax(a: widget->fontMetrics().height(), b: int(QStyleHelper::dpiScaled(value: 13, option: opt)));
4506#endif
4507 } else {
4508 ret = qMax(a: widget ? widget->fontMetrics().height() : opt->fontMetrics.height(), b: 18);
4509 }
4510 } else {
4511 ret = int(QStyleHelper::dpiScaled(value: 18., option: opt));
4512 }
4513 break;
4514 }
4515 case PM_TitleBarButtonSize:
4516 ret = int(QStyleHelper::dpiScaled(value: 16., option: opt));
4517 break;
4518 case PM_TitleBarButtonIconSize:
4519 ret = int(QStyleHelper::dpiScaled(value: 16., option: opt));
4520 break;
4521
4522 case PM_ScrollBarSliderMin:
4523 ret = int(QStyleHelper::dpiScaled(value: 9., option: opt));
4524 break;
4525
4526 case PM_ButtonMargin:
4527 ret = int(QStyleHelper::dpiScaled(value: 6., option: opt));
4528 break;
4529
4530 case PM_DockWidgetTitleBarButtonMargin:
4531 ret = int(QStyleHelper::dpiScaled(value: 2., option: opt));
4532 break;
4533
4534 case PM_ButtonDefaultIndicator:
4535 ret = 0;
4536 break;
4537
4538 case PM_MenuButtonIndicator:
4539 ret = int(QStyleHelper::dpiScaled(value: 12, option: opt));
4540 break;
4541
4542 case PM_ButtonShiftHorizontal:
4543 case PM_ButtonShiftVertical:
4544
4545 case PM_DefaultFrameWidth:
4546 ret = 2;
4547 break;
4548
4549 case PM_ComboBoxFrameWidth:
4550 case PM_SpinBoxFrameWidth:
4551 case PM_MenuPanelWidth:
4552 case PM_TabBarBaseOverlap:
4553 case PM_TabBarBaseHeight:
4554 ret = proxy()->pixelMetric(metric: PM_DefaultFrameWidth, option: opt, widget);
4555 break;
4556
4557 case PM_MdiSubWindowFrameWidth:
4558 ret = int(QStyleHelper::dpiScaled(value: 4, option: opt));
4559 break;
4560
4561 case PM_MdiSubWindowMinimizedWidth:
4562 ret = int(QStyleHelper::dpiScaled(value: 196, option: opt));
4563 break;
4564
4565#if QT_CONFIG(scrollbar)
4566 case PM_ScrollBarExtent:
4567 if (qstyleoption_cast<const QStyleOptionSlider *>(opt))
4568 ret = 16;
4569 else
4570 ret = int(QStyleHelper::dpiScaled(value: 16, option: opt));
4571 break;
4572#endif
4573 case PM_MaximumDragDistance:
4574 ret = QGuiApplicationPrivate::platformTheme()->themeHint(hint: QPlatformTheme::MaximumScrollBarDragDistance).toInt();
4575 break;
4576
4577#if QT_CONFIG(slider)
4578 case PM_SliderThickness:
4579 ret = int(QStyleHelper::dpiScaled(value: 16, option: opt));
4580 break;
4581
4582 case PM_SliderTickmarkOffset:
4583 if (const QStyleOptionSlider *sl = qstyleoption_cast<const QStyleOptionSlider *>(opt)) {
4584 int space = (sl->orientation == Qt::Horizontal) ? sl->rect.height()
4585 : sl->rect.width();
4586 int thickness = proxy()->pixelMetric(metric: PM_SliderControlThickness, option: sl, widget);
4587 int ticks = sl->tickPosition;
4588
4589 if (ticks == QSlider::TicksBothSides)
4590 ret = (space - thickness) / 2;
4591 else if (ticks == QSlider::TicksAbove)
4592 ret = space - thickness;
4593 else
4594 ret = 0;
4595 } else {
4596 ret = 0;
4597 }
4598 break;
4599
4600 case PM_SliderSpaceAvailable:
4601 if (const QStyleOptionSlider *sl = qstyleoption_cast<const QStyleOptionSlider *>(opt)) {
4602 if (sl->orientation == Qt::Horizontal)
4603 ret = sl->rect.width() - proxy()->pixelMetric(metric: PM_SliderLength, option: sl, widget);
4604 else
4605 ret = sl->rect.height() - proxy()->pixelMetric(metric: PM_SliderLength, option: sl, widget);
4606 } else {
4607 ret = 0;
4608 }
4609 break;
4610#endif // QT_CONFIG(slider)
4611#if QT_CONFIG(dockwidget)
4612 case PM_DockWidgetSeparatorExtent:
4613 ret = int(QStyleHelper::dpiScaled(value: 6, option: opt));
4614 break;
4615
4616 case PM_DockWidgetHandleExtent:
4617 ret = int(QStyleHelper::dpiScaled(value: 8, option: opt));
4618 break;
4619 case PM_DockWidgetTitleMargin:
4620 ret = 0;
4621 break;
4622 case PM_DockWidgetFrameWidth:
4623 ret = 1;
4624 break;
4625#endif // QT_CONFIG(dockwidget)
4626
4627 case PM_SpinBoxSliderHeight:
4628 case PM_MenuBarPanelWidth:
4629 ret = 2;
4630 break;
4631
4632 case PM_MenuBarItemSpacing:
4633 ret = 0;
4634 break;
4635
4636#if QT_CONFIG(toolbar)
4637 case PM_ToolBarFrameWidth:
4638 ret = 1;
4639 break;
4640
4641 case PM_ToolBarItemMargin:
4642 ret = 0;
4643 break;
4644
4645 case PM_ToolBarItemSpacing:
4646 ret = int(QStyleHelper::dpiScaled(value: 4, option: opt));
4647 break;
4648
4649 case PM_ToolBarHandleExtent:
4650 ret = int(QStyleHelper::dpiScaled(value: 8, option: opt));
4651 break;
4652
4653 case PM_ToolBarSeparatorExtent:
4654 ret = int(QStyleHelper::dpiScaled(value: 6, option: opt));
4655 break;
4656
4657 case PM_ToolBarExtensionExtent:
4658 ret = int(QStyleHelper::dpiScaled(value: 12, option: opt));
4659 break;
4660#endif // QT_CONFIG(toolbar)
4661
4662#if QT_CONFIG(tabbar)
4663 case PM_TabBarTabOverlap:
4664 ret = 3;
4665 break;
4666
4667 case PM_TabBarTabHSpace:
4668 ret = int(QStyleHelper::dpiScaled(value: 24, option: opt));
4669 break;
4670
4671 case PM_TabBarTabShiftHorizontal:
4672 ret = 0;
4673 break;
4674
4675 case PM_TabBarTabShiftVertical:
4676 ret = 2;
4677 break;
4678
4679 case PM_TabBarTabVSpace:
4680 {
4681 const QStyleOptionTab *tb = qstyleoption_cast<const QStyleOptionTab *>(opt);
4682 if (tb && (tb->shape == QTabBar::RoundedNorth || tb->shape == QTabBar::RoundedSouth
4683 || tb->shape == QTabBar::RoundedWest || tb->shape == QTabBar::RoundedEast))
4684 ret = 8;
4685 else
4686 if (tb && (tb->shape == QTabBar::TriangularWest || tb->shape == QTabBar::TriangularEast))
4687 ret = 3;
4688 else
4689 ret = 2;
4690 break;
4691 }
4692#endif
4693
4694 case PM_ProgressBarChunkWidth:
4695 ret = 9;
4696 break;
4697
4698 case PM_IndicatorWidth:
4699 ret = int(QStyleHelper::dpiScaled(value: 13, option: opt));
4700 break;
4701
4702 case PM_IndicatorHeight:
4703 ret = int(QStyleHelper::dpiScaled(value: 13, option: opt));
4704 break;
4705
4706 case PM_ExclusiveIndicatorWidth:
4707 ret = int(QStyleHelper::dpiScaled(value: 12, option: opt));
4708 break;
4709
4710 case PM_ExclusiveIndicatorHeight:
4711 ret = int(QStyleHelper::dpiScaled(value: 12, option: opt));
4712 break;
4713
4714 case PM_MenuTearoffHeight:
4715 ret = int(QStyleHelper::dpiScaled(value: 10, option: opt));
4716 break;
4717
4718 case PM_MenuScrollerHeight:
4719 ret = int(QStyleHelper::dpiScaled(value: 10, option: opt));
4720 break;
4721
4722 case PM_MenuDesktopFrameWidth:
4723 case PM_MenuHMargin:
4724 case PM_MenuVMargin:
4725 ret = 0;
4726 break;
4727
4728 case PM_HeaderMargin:
4729 ret = int(QStyleHelper::dpiScaled(value: 4, option: opt));
4730 break;
4731 case PM_HeaderMarkSize:
4732 ret = int(QStyleHelper::dpiScaled(value: 16, option: opt));
4733 break;
4734 case PM_HeaderGripMargin:
4735 ret = int(QStyleHelper::dpiScaled(value: 4, option: opt));
4736 break;
4737 case PM_HeaderDefaultSectionSizeHorizontal:
4738 ret = int(QStyleHelper::dpiScaled(value: 100, option: opt));
4739 break;
4740 case PM_HeaderDefaultSectionSizeVertical:
4741 ret = int(QStyleHelper::dpiScaled(value: 30, option: opt));
4742 break;
4743 case PM_TabBarScrollButtonWidth:
4744 ret = int(QStyleHelper::dpiScaled(value: 16, option: opt));
4745 break;
4746 case PM_LayoutLeftMargin:
4747 case PM_LayoutTopMargin:
4748 case PM_LayoutRightMargin:
4749 case PM_LayoutBottomMargin:
4750 {
4751 bool isWindow = false;
4752 if (opt) {
4753 isWindow = (opt->state & State_Window);
4754 } else if (widget) {
4755 isWindow = widget->isWindow();
4756 }
4757 ret = int(QStyleHelper::dpiScaled(value: isWindow ? 11 : 9, option: opt));
4758 break;
4759 }
4760 case PM_LayoutHorizontalSpacing:
4761 case PM_LayoutVerticalSpacing:
4762 ret = int(QStyleHelper::dpiScaled(value: 6, option: opt));
4763 break;
4764
4765 case PM_ToolBarIconSize:
4766 ret = 0;
4767 if (const QPlatformTheme *theme = QGuiApplicationPrivate::platformTheme())
4768 ret = theme->themeHint(hint: QPlatformTheme::ToolBarIconSize).toInt();
4769 if (ret <= 0)
4770 ret = int(QStyleHelper::dpiScaled(value: 24, option: opt));
4771 break;
4772
4773 case PM_TabBarIconSize:
4774 ret = proxy()->pixelMetric(metric: PM_SmallIconSize, option: opt, widget);
4775 break;
4776 case PM_ListViewIconSize:
4777#if QT_CONFIG(filedialog)
4778 if (qobject_cast<const QSidebar *>(object: widget))
4779 ret = int(QStyleHelper::dpiScaled(value: 24., option: opt));
4780 else
4781#endif
4782 ret = proxy()->pixelMetric(metric: PM_SmallIconSize, option: opt, widget);
4783 break;
4784
4785 case PM_ButtonIconSize:
4786 case PM_SmallIconSize:
4787 ret = int(QStyleHelper::dpiScaled(value: 16, option: opt));
4788 break;
4789 case PM_IconViewIconSize:
4790 ret = proxy()->pixelMetric(metric: PM_LargeIconSize, option: opt, widget);
4791 break;
4792 case PM_LineEditIconSize:
4793 ret = proxy()->pixelMetric(metric: PM_SmallIconSize, option: opt, widget);
4794 break;
4795 case PM_LineEditIconMargin:
4796 ret = proxy()->pixelMetric(metric: PM_LineEditIconSize, option: opt, widget) / 4;
4797 break;
4798
4799 case PM_LargeIconSize:
4800 ret = int(QStyleHelper::dpiScaled(value: 32, option: opt));
4801 break;
4802
4803 case PM_ToolTipLabelFrameWidth:
4804 ret = 1;
4805 break;
4806 case PM_CheckBoxLabelSpacing:
4807 case PM_RadioButtonLabelSpacing:
4808 ret = int(QStyleHelper::dpiScaled(value: 6, option: opt));
4809 break;
4810 case PM_SizeGripSize:
4811 ret = int(QStyleHelper::dpiScaled(value: 13, option: opt));
4812 break;
4813 case PM_MessageBoxIconSize:
4814#ifdef Q_OS_MAC
4815 if (QGuiApplication::desktopSettingsAware()) {
4816 ret = 64; // No DPI scaling, it's handled elsewhere.
4817 } else
4818#endif
4819 {
4820 ret = int(QStyleHelper::dpiScaled(value: 32, option: opt));
4821 }
4822 break;
4823 case PM_TextCursorWidth:
4824 ret = QGuiApplicationPrivate::platformTheme()->themeHint(hint: QPlatformTheme::TextCursorWidth).toInt();
4825 break;
4826 case PM_TabBar_ScrollButtonOverlap:
4827 ret = 1;
4828 break;
4829 case PM_TabCloseIndicatorWidth:
4830 case PM_TabCloseIndicatorHeight:
4831 ret = int(QStyleHelper::dpiScaled(value: 16, option: opt));
4832 break;
4833 case PM_ScrollView_ScrollBarSpacing:
4834 ret = 2 * proxy()->pixelMetric(metric: PM_DefaultFrameWidth, option: opt, widget);
4835 break;
4836 case PM_ScrollView_ScrollBarOverlap:
4837 ret = 0;
4838 break;
4839 case PM_SubMenuOverlap:
4840 ret = -proxy()->pixelMetric(metric: QStyle::PM_MenuPanelWidth, option: opt, widget);
4841 break;
4842 case PM_TreeViewIndentation:
4843 ret = int(QStyleHelper::dpiScaled(value: 20, option: opt));
4844 break;
4845 default:
4846 ret = 0;
4847 break;
4848 }
4849
4850 return ret;
4851}
4852
4853/*!
4854 \reimp
4855*/
4856QSize QCommonStyle::sizeFromContents(ContentsType contentsType, const QStyleOption *opt,
4857 const QSize &contentsSize, const QWidget *widget) const
4858{
4859 Q_D(const QCommonStyle);
4860 QSize size(contentsSize);
4861 switch (contentsType) {
4862 case CT_PushButton:
4863 if (const auto *buttonOpt = qstyleoption_cast<const QStyleOptionButton *>(opt)) {
4864 int width = contentsSize.width();
4865 int height = contentsSize.height();
4866 const int buttonMargin = proxy()->pixelMetric(metric: PM_ButtonMargin, option: buttonOpt, widget);
4867 const int defaultFrameWidth = proxy()->pixelMetric(metric: PM_DefaultFrameWidth, option: buttonOpt, widget) * 2;
4868 width += buttonMargin + defaultFrameWidth;
4869 height += buttonMargin + defaultFrameWidth;
4870 if (buttonOpt->features.testFlag(flag: QStyleOptionButton::AutoDefaultButton)) {
4871 const int buttonIndicator = proxy()->pixelMetric(metric: PM_ButtonDefaultIndicator,
4872 option: buttonOpt,
4873 widget) * 2;
4874 width += buttonIndicator;
4875 height += buttonIndicator;
4876 }
4877 size = QSize(width, height);
4878 }
4879 break;
4880 case CT_RadioButton:
4881 case CT_CheckBox:
4882 if (const auto *buttonOpt = qstyleoption_cast<const QStyleOptionButton *>(opt)) {
4883 const bool isRadio = (contentsType == CT_RadioButton);
4884
4885 const int width = proxy()->pixelMetric(metric: isRadio ? PM_ExclusiveIndicatorWidth
4886 : PM_IndicatorWidth, option: buttonOpt, widget);
4887 const int height = proxy()->pixelMetric(metric: isRadio ? PM_ExclusiveIndicatorHeight
4888 : PM_IndicatorHeight, option: buttonOpt, widget);
4889
4890 int margins = 0;
4891
4892 // we add 4 pixels for label margins
4893 if (!buttonOpt->icon.isNull() || !buttonOpt->text.isEmpty()) {
4894 margins = 4 + proxy()->pixelMetric(metric: isRadio ? PM_RadioButtonLabelSpacing
4895 : PM_CheckBoxLabelSpacing, option: opt, widget);
4896 }
4897
4898 size += QSize(width + margins, 4);
4899 size.setHeight(qMax(a: size.height(), b: height));
4900 }
4901 break;
4902#if QT_CONFIG(menu)
4903 case CT_MenuItem:
4904 if (const auto *menuItemOpt = qstyleoption_cast<const QStyleOptionMenuItem *>(opt)) {
4905 const bool checkable = menuItemOpt->menuHasCheckableItems;
4906 const int maxpmw = menuItemOpt->maxIconWidth;
4907 int width = size.width();
4908 int height;
4909 if (menuItemOpt->menuItemType == QStyleOptionMenuItem::Separator) {
4910 width = 10;
4911 height = 2;
4912 } else {
4913 height = menuItemOpt->fontMetrics.height() + 8;
4914 if (!menuItemOpt->icon.isNull()) {
4915 int iconExtent = proxy()->pixelMetric(metric: PM_SmallIconSize, option: opt);
4916 height = qMax(a: height,
4917 b: menuItemOpt->icon.actualSize(size: QSize(iconExtent,
4918 iconExtent)).height() + 4);
4919 }
4920 }
4921 if (menuItemOpt->text.contains(c: u'\t'))
4922 width += 12;
4923 if (maxpmw > 0)
4924 width += maxpmw + 6;
4925 if (checkable && maxpmw < 20)
4926 width += 20 - maxpmw;
4927 if (checkable || maxpmw > 0)
4928 width += 2;
4929 width += 12;
4930 size = QSize(width, height);
4931 }
4932 break;
4933#endif // QT_CONFIG(menu)
4934#if QT_CONFIG(toolbutton)
4935 case CT_ToolButton:
4936 size = QSize(size.width() + 6, size.height() + 5);
4937 break;
4938#endif // QT_CONFIG(toolbutton)
4939#if QT_CONFIG(combobox)
4940 case CT_ComboBox:
4941 if (const auto *comboBoxOpt = qstyleoption_cast<const QStyleOptionComboBox *>(opt)) {
4942 const int frameWidth = comboBoxOpt->frame ? proxy()->pixelMetric(metric: PM_ComboBoxFrameWidth,
4943 option: opt,
4944 widget) * 2 : 0;
4945 const int textMargins = 2*(proxy()->pixelMetric(metric: PM_FocusFrameHMargin, option: opt) + 1);
4946
4947 // QItemDelegate::sizeHint expands the textMargins two times, thus the 2*textMargins...
4948 const int other = qMax(a: 23, b: 2 * textMargins
4949 + proxy()->pixelMetric(metric: QStyle::PM_ScrollBarExtent,
4950 option: opt, widget));
4951
4952 size = QSize(size.width() + frameWidth + other, size.height() + frameWidth);
4953 }
4954 break;
4955#endif // QT_CONFIG(combobox)
4956 case CT_HeaderSection:
4957 if (const auto *headerOpt = qstyleoption_cast<const QStyleOptionHeader *>(opt)) {
4958 const bool nullIcon = headerOpt->icon.isNull();
4959 const int margin = proxy()->pixelMetric(metric: QStyle::PM_HeaderMargin, option: headerOpt, widget);
4960 const int iconSize = nullIcon ? 0 : proxy()->pixelMetric(metric: QStyle::PM_SmallIconSize,
4961 option: headerOpt,
4962 widget);
4963 const QSize textSize = headerOpt->fontMetrics.size(flags: 0, str: headerOpt->text);
4964 size.setHeight(margin + qMax(a: iconSize, b: textSize.height()) + margin);
4965 size.setWidth((nullIcon ? 0 : margin) + iconSize
4966 + (headerOpt->text.isNull() ? 0 : margin) + textSize.width() + margin);
4967 if (headerOpt->sortIndicator != QStyleOptionHeader::None) {
4968 const int margin = proxy()->pixelMetric(metric: QStyle::PM_HeaderMargin, option: headerOpt, widget);
4969 if (headerOpt->orientation == Qt::Horizontal)
4970 size.rwidth() += size.height() + margin;
4971 else
4972 size.rheight() += size.width() + margin;
4973 }
4974 }
4975 break;
4976 case CT_TabWidget:
4977 size += QSize(4, 4);
4978 break;
4979 case CT_LineEdit:
4980 if (const auto *frameOpt = qstyleoption_cast<const QStyleOptionFrame *>(opt))
4981 size += QSize(2 * frameOpt->lineWidth, 2 * frameOpt->lineWidth);
4982 break;
4983#if QT_CONFIG(groupbox)
4984 case CT_GroupBox:
4985 if (const auto *groupBoxOpt = qstyleoption_cast<const QStyleOptionGroupBox *>(opt))
4986 size += QSize(groupBoxOpt->features.testFlag(flag: QStyleOptionFrame::Flat) ? 0 : 16, 0);
4987 break;
4988#endif // QT_CONFIG(groupbox)
4989 case CT_MdiControls:
4990 if (const auto *styleOpt = qstyleoption_cast<const QStyleOptionComplex *>(opt)) {
4991 const int buttonSize = proxy()->pixelMetric(metric: PM_TitleBarButtonSize, option: styleOpt, widget);
4992 int width = 1;
4993 if (styleOpt->subControls & SC_MdiMinButton)
4994 width += buttonSize + 1;
4995 if (styleOpt->subControls & SC_MdiNormalButton)
4996 width += buttonSize + 1;
4997 if (styleOpt->subControls & SC_MdiCloseButton)
4998 width += buttonSize + 1;
4999 size = QSize(width, buttonSize);
5000 } else {
5001 const int buttonSize = proxy()->pixelMetric(metric: PM_TitleBarButtonSize, option: opt, widget);
5002 size = QSize(1 + 3 * (buttonSize + 1), buttonSize);
5003 }
5004 break;
5005#if QT_CONFIG(itemviews)
5006 case CT_ItemViewItem:
5007 if (const auto *viewItemOpt = qstyleoption_cast<const QStyleOptionViewItem *>(opt)) {
5008 QRect decorationRect, displayRect, checkRect;
5009 d->viewItemLayout(opt: viewItemOpt, checkRect: &checkRect, pixmapRect: &decorationRect, textRect: &displayRect, sizehint: true);
5010 size = (decorationRect|displayRect|checkRect).size();
5011 if (decorationRect.isValid() && size.height() == decorationRect.height())
5012 size.rheight() += 2; // Prevent icons from overlapping.
5013 }
5014 break;
5015#else
5016 Q_UNUSED(d);
5017#endif // QT_CONFIG(itemviews)
5018#if QT_CONFIG(spinbox)
5019 case CT_SpinBox:
5020 if (const auto *spinBoxOpt = qstyleoption_cast<const QStyleOptionSpinBox *>(opt)) {
5021 // Add button + frame widths
5022 const qreal dpi = QStyleHelper::dpi(option: opt);
5023 const bool hasButtons = (spinBoxOpt->buttonSymbols != QAbstractSpinBox::NoButtons);
5024 const int buttonWidth = hasButtons ? qRound(d: QStyleHelper::dpiScaled(value: 16, dpi)) : 0;
5025 const int frameWidth = spinBoxOpt->frame ? proxy()->pixelMetric(metric: PM_SpinBoxFrameWidth,
5026 option: spinBoxOpt, widget) : 0;
5027
5028 size += QSize(buttonWidth + 2 * frameWidth, 2 * frameWidth);
5029 }
5030 break;
5031#endif
5032 case CT_ScrollBar:
5033 case CT_MenuBar:
5034 case CT_Menu:
5035 case CT_MenuBarItem:
5036 case CT_Slider:
5037 case CT_ProgressBar:
5038 case CT_TabBarTab:
5039 // just return the contentsSize for now
5040 Q_FALLTHROUGH();
5041 default:
5042 break;
5043 }
5044 return size;
5045}
5046
5047
5048/*! \reimp */
5049int QCommonStyle::styleHint(StyleHint sh, const QStyleOption *opt, const QWidget *widget,
5050 QStyleHintReturn *hret) const
5051{
5052 int ret = 0;
5053
5054 switch (sh) {
5055 case SH_Menu_KeyboardSearch:
5056 ret = false;
5057 break;
5058 case SH_Slider_AbsoluteSetButtons:
5059 ret = Qt::MiddleButton;
5060 break;
5061 case SH_Slider_PageSetButtons:
5062 ret = Qt::LeftButton;
5063 break;
5064 case SH_ScrollBar_ContextMenu:
5065 ret = true;
5066 break;
5067#if QT_CONFIG(dialogbuttonbox)
5068 case SH_DialogButtons_DefaultButton: // This value not used anywhere.
5069 ret = QDialogButtonBox::AcceptRole;
5070 break;
5071#endif
5072#if QT_CONFIG(groupbox)
5073 case SH_GroupBox_TextLabelVerticalAlignment:
5074 ret = Qt::AlignVCenter;
5075 break;
5076
5077 case SH_GroupBox_TextLabelColor:
5078 ret = opt ? int(opt->palette.color(cr: QPalette::Text).rgba()) : 0;
5079 break;
5080#endif // QT_CONFIG(groupbox)
5081
5082 case SH_ListViewExpand_SelectMouseType:
5083 case SH_TabBar_SelectMouseType:
5084 ret = QEvent::MouseButtonPress;
5085 break;
5086
5087
5088 case SH_TabBar_Alignment:
5089 ret = Qt::AlignLeft;
5090 break;
5091
5092 case SH_Header_ArrowAlignment:
5093 ret = Qt::AlignRight | Qt::AlignVCenter;
5094 break;
5095
5096 case SH_TitleBar_AutoRaise:
5097 ret = false;
5098 break;
5099
5100 case SH_Menu_SubMenuPopupDelay:
5101 ret = 256;
5102 break;
5103
5104 case SH_Menu_SloppySubMenus:
5105 ret = true;
5106 break;
5107
5108 case SH_Menu_SubMenuUniDirection:
5109 ret = false;
5110 break;
5111 case SH_Menu_SubMenuUniDirectionFailCount:
5112 ret = 1;
5113 break;
5114 case SH_Menu_SubMenuSloppySelectOtherActions:
5115 ret = true;
5116 break;
5117 case SH_Menu_SubMenuSloppyCloseTimeout:
5118 ret = 1000;
5119 break;
5120 case SH_Menu_SubMenuResetWhenReenteringParent:
5121 ret = false;
5122 break;
5123 case SH_Menu_SubMenuDontStartSloppyOnLeave:
5124 ret = false;
5125 break;
5126
5127 case SH_ProgressDialog_TextLabelAlignment:
5128 ret = Qt::AlignCenter;
5129 break;
5130
5131 case SH_BlinkCursorWhenTextSelected:
5132#if defined(Q_OS_DARWIN)
5133 ret = 0;
5134#else
5135 ret = 1;
5136#endif
5137 break;
5138
5139 case SH_Table_GridLineColor:
5140 if (opt)
5141 ret = opt->palette.color(cr: QPalette::Mid).rgba();
5142 else
5143 ret = -1;
5144 break;
5145 case SH_LineEdit_PasswordCharacter: {
5146 const QPlatformTheme *theme = QGuiApplicationPrivate::platformTheme();
5147 const QPlatformTheme::ThemeHint hintType = QPlatformTheme::PasswordMaskCharacter;
5148 const QVariant hint = theme ? theme->themeHint(hint: hintType) : QPlatformTheme::defaultThemeHint(hint: hintType);
5149 ret = hint.toChar().unicode();
5150 break;
5151 }
5152 case SH_LineEdit_PasswordMaskDelay:
5153 ret = QGuiApplicationPrivate::platformTheme()->themeHint(hint: QPlatformTheme::PasswordMaskDelay).toInt();
5154 break;
5155 case SH_ToolBox_SelectedPageTitleBold:
5156 ret = 1;
5157 break;
5158
5159 case SH_UnderlineShortcut:
5160 ret = 1;
5161 break;
5162
5163 case SH_SpinBox_ClickAutoRepeatRate:
5164 ret = 150;
5165 break;
5166
5167 case SH_SpinBox_ClickAutoRepeatThreshold:
5168 ret = 500;
5169 break;
5170
5171 case SH_SpinBox_KeyPressAutoRepeatRate:
5172 ret = 75;
5173 break;
5174
5175 case SH_Menu_SelectionWrap:
5176 ret = true;
5177 break;
5178
5179 case SH_Menu_FillScreenWithScroll:
5180 ret = true;
5181 break;
5182
5183 case SH_ToolTipLabel_Opacity:
5184 ret = 255;
5185 break;
5186
5187 case SH_Button_FocusPolicy:
5188 ret = Qt::StrongFocus;
5189 break;
5190
5191 case SH_MessageBox_UseBorderForButtonSpacing:
5192 ret = 0;
5193 break;
5194
5195 case SH_ToolButton_PopupDelay:
5196 ret = 600;
5197 break;
5198
5199 case SH_FocusFrame_Mask:
5200 ret = 1;
5201 if (widget) {
5202 if (QStyleHintReturnMask *mask = qstyleoption_cast<QStyleHintReturnMask*>(hint: hret)) {
5203 mask->region = widget->rect();
5204 const int vmargin = proxy()->pixelMetric(metric: QStyle::PM_FocusFrameVMargin, option: opt);
5205 const int hmargin = proxy()->pixelMetric(metric: QStyle::PM_FocusFrameHMargin, option: opt);
5206 mask->region -= QRect(widget->rect().adjusted(xp1: hmargin, yp1: vmargin, xp2: -hmargin, yp2: -vmargin));
5207 }
5208 }
5209 break;
5210#if QT_CONFIG(rubberband)
5211 case SH_RubberBand_Mask:
5212 if (const QStyleOptionRubberBand *rbOpt = qstyleoption_cast<const QStyleOptionRubberBand *>(opt)) {
5213 ret = 0;
5214 if (rbOpt->shape == QRubberBand::Rectangle) {
5215 ret = true;
5216 if (QStyleHintReturnMask *mask = qstyleoption_cast<QStyleHintReturnMask*>(hint: hret)) {
5217 mask->region = opt->rect;
5218 const int margin = proxy()->pixelMetric(metric: PM_DefaultFrameWidth, option: opt) * 2;
5219 mask->region -= opt->rect.adjusted(xp1: margin, yp1: margin, xp2: -margin, yp2: -margin);
5220 }
5221 }
5222 }
5223 break;
5224#endif // QT_CONFIG(rubberband)
5225 case SH_SpinControls_DisableOnBounds:
5226 ret = 1;
5227 break;
5228
5229 case SH_Dial_BackgroundRole:
5230 ret = QPalette::Window;
5231 break;
5232
5233 case SH_ComboBox_LayoutDirection:
5234 ret = opt ? opt->direction : Qt::LeftToRight;
5235 break;
5236
5237 case SH_ItemView_EllipsisLocation:
5238 ret = Qt::AlignTrailing;
5239 break;
5240
5241 case SH_ItemView_ShowDecorationSelected:
5242 ret = false;
5243 break;
5244
5245 case SH_ItemView_ActivateItemOnSingleClick:
5246 ret = 0;
5247 if (const QPlatformTheme *theme = QGuiApplicationPrivate::platformTheme())
5248 ret = theme->themeHint(hint: QPlatformTheme::ItemViewActivateItemOnSingleClick).toBool() ? 1 : 0;
5249 break;
5250 case SH_TitleBar_ModifyNotification:
5251 ret = true;
5252 break;

5255 break;

5258 break;

5264 break;
5265#endif
5266 case SH_ComboBox_PopupFrameStyle:
5267 ret = QFrame::StyledPanel | QFrame::Plain;
5268 break;
5269 case SH_MessageBox_TextInteractionFlags:
5270 ret = Qt::LinksAccessibleByMouse;
5271 break;

5274 if (const QPlatformTheme *theme = QGuiApplicationPrivate::platformTheme())
5275 ret = theme->themeHint(hint: QPlatformTheme::DialogButtonBoxButtonsHaveIcons).toBool() ? 1 : 0;
5276 break;

5279 break;
5280 case SH_ItemView_MovementWithoutUpdatingSelection:
5281 ret = true;
5282 break;
5283 case SH_FocusFrame_AboveWidget:
5284 ret = false;
5285 break;

5287 case SH_TabWidget_DefaultTabPosition:

5289 break;
5290#endif
5291 case SH_ToolBar_Movable:
5292 ret = true;
5293 break;

5295 ret = true;

5302 break;

5306 break;

5321 break;

5372 break;

5386 break;
5387 case SH_ComboBox_AllowWheelScrolling:

5389 break;
5390 case SH_SpinBox_ButtonsInsideFrame:

5452
5453#if QT_CONFIG(imageformat_xpm)
5454static QPixmap cachedPixmapFromXPM(const char * const *xpm)
5455{
5456 QPixmap result;
5457 const QString tag = QString::asprintf(format: "xpm:0x%p", static_cast<const void*>(xpm));
5458 if (!QPixmapCache::find(key: tag, pixmap: &result)) {
5459 result = QPixmap(xpm);
5460 QPixmapCache::insert(key: tag, pixmap: result);
5461 }
5462 return result;
5463}
5464
5465static inline QPixmap titleBarMenuCachedPixmapFromXPM() { return cachedPixmapFromXPM(xpm: qt_menu_xpm); }
5466#endif // QT_CONFIG(imageformat_xpm)

5468#ifndef QT_NO_IMAGEFORMAT_PNG
5469static inline QString clearText16IconPath()
5470{
5471 return QStringLiteral(":/qt-project.org/styles/commonstyle/images/cleartext-16.png");
5472}
5473#endif // !QT_NO_IMAGEFORMAT_PNG
5474
5475#if defined(Q_OS_WIN) || QT_CONFIG(imageformat_png)
5476static QIcon clearTextIcon(bool rtl)
5477{
5478 const QString directionalThemeName = rtl
5479 ? QStringLiteral("edit-clear-locationbar-ltr") : QStringLiteral("edit-clear-locationbar-rtl");
5480 if (QIcon::hasThemeIcon(name: directionalThemeName))
5481 return QIcon::fromTheme(name: directionalThemeName);
5482 const QString themeName = QStringLiteral("edit-clear");
5483 if (QIcon::hasThemeIcon(name: themeName))
5484 return QIcon::fromTheme(name: themeName);
5485
5486 QIcon icon;
5487#ifndef QT_NO_IMAGEFORMAT_PNG
5488 QPixmap clearText16(clearText16IconPath());
5489 Q_ASSERT(!clearText16.size().isEmpty());
5490 icon.addPixmap(pixmap: clearText16);
5491 QPixmap clearText32(QStringLiteral(":/qt-project.org/styles/commonstyle/images/cleartext-32.png"));
5492 Q_ASSERT(!clearText32.size().isEmpty());
5493 icon.addPixmap(pixmap: clearText32);
5494 clearText32.setDevicePixelRatio(2); // The 32x32 pixmap can also be used for 16x16/devicePixelRatio=2
5495 icon.addPixmap(pixmap: clearText32);
5496#endif // !QT_NO_IMAGEFORMAT_PNG
5497 return icon;
5498}
5499#endif

5844 return QPixmap();
5845}
5846
5847#if QT_CONFIG(imageformat_png)
5848static inline QString iconResourcePrefix() { return QStringLiteral(":/qt-project.org/styles/commonstyle/images/"); }
5849static inline QString iconPngSuffix() { return QStringLiteral(".png"); }
5850
5851static void addIconFiles(const QString &prefix, const int sizes[], size_t count, QIcon &icon)
5852{
5853 for (size_t i = 0; i < count; ++i)
5854 icon.addFile(fileName: prefix + QString::number(sizes[i]) + iconPngSuffix());
5855}

5858static const int titleBarSizes[] = {16, 32, 48};
5859static const int toolBarExtHSizes[] = {8, 16, 32};
5860static const int toolBarExtVSizes[] = {5, 10, 20};
5861#endif // imageformat_png

5888 if (const QPlatformTheme *theme = QGuiApplicationPrivate::platformTheme()) {
5889 QPlatformTheme::StandardPixmap sp = static_cast<QPlatformTheme::StandardPixmap>(standardIcon);
5890 for (int size = 16 ; size <= 32 ; size += 16) {

5892 icon.addPixmap(pixmap, QIcon::Normal);

5895 break;
5896 case SP_DirIcon:

5901 QPlatformTheme::DirLinkOpenIcon;

5905 icon.addPixmap(pixmap, QIcon::Normal, QIcon::Off);
5906 pixmap = theme->standardPixmap(spOn, pixSize);
5907 icon.addPixmap(pixmap, QIcon::Normal, QIcon::On);

6437
6438static inline uint qt_intensity(uint r, uint g, uint b)
6439{
6440 // 30% red, 59% green, 11% blue
6441 return (77 * r + 150 * g + 28 * b) / 255;
6442}
6443
6444/*! \reimp */
6445QPixmap QCommonStyle::generatedIconPixmap(QIcon::Mode iconMode, const QPixmap &pixmap,
6446 const QStyleOption *opt) const
6447{
6448 switch (iconMode) {
6449 case QIcon::Disabled: {
6450 QImage im = pixmap.toImage().convertToFormat(f: QImage::Format_ARGB32);
6451
6452 // Create a colortable based on the background (black -> bg -> white)
6453 QColor bg = opt->palette.color(cg: QPalette::Disabled, cr: QPalette::Window);
6454 int red = bg.red();
6455 int green = bg.green();
6456 int blue = bg.blue();
6457 uchar reds[256], greens[256], blues[256];
6458 for (int i=0; i<128; ++i) {
6459 reds[i] = uchar((red * (i<<1)) >> 8);
6460 greens[i] = uchar((green * (i<<1)) >> 8);
6461 blues[i] = uchar((blue * (i<<1)) >> 8);
6462 }
6463 for (int i=0; i<128; ++i) {
6464 reds[i+128] = uchar(qMin(a: red + (i << 1), b: 255));
6465 greens[i+128] = uchar(qMin(a: green + (i << 1), b: 255));
6466 blues[i+128] = uchar(qMin(a: blue + (i << 1), b: 255));
6467 }
6468
6469 int intensity = qt_intensity(r: red, g: green, b: blue);
6470 const int factor = 191;
6471
6472 // High intensity colors needs dark shifting in the color table, while
6473 // low intensity colors needs light shifting. This is to increase the
6474 // perceived contrast.
6475 if ((red - factor > green && red - factor > blue)
6476 || (green - factor > red && green - factor > blue)
6477 || (blue - factor > red && blue - factor > green))
6478 intensity = qMin(a: 255, b: intensity + 91);
6479 else if (intensity <= 128)
6480 intensity -= 51;
6481
6482 for (int y=0; y<im.height(); ++y) {
6483 QRgb *scanLine = (QRgb*)im.scanLine(y);
6484 for (int x=0; x<im.width(); ++x) {
6485 QRgb pixel = *scanLine;
6486 // Calculate color table index, taking intensity adjustment
6487 // and a magic offset into account.
6488 uint ci = uint(qGray(rgb: pixel)/3 + (130 - intensity / 3));
6489 *scanLine = qRgba(r: reds[ci], g: greens[ci], b: blues[ci], a: qAlpha(rgb: pixel));
6490 ++scanLine;
6491 }
6492 }
6493
6494 return QPixmap::fromImage(image: im);
6495 }
6496 case QIcon::Selected: {
6497 QImage img = pixmap.toImage().convertToFormat(f: QImage::Format_ARGB32_Premultiplied);
6498 QColor color = opt->palette.color(cg: QPalette::Normal, cr: QPalette::Highlight);
6499 color.setAlphaF(0.3f);
6500 QPainter painter(&img);
6501 painter.setCompositionMode(QPainter::CompositionMode_SourceAtop);
6502 painter.fillRect(x: 0, y: 0, w: img.width(), h: img.height(), b: color);
6503 painter.end();
6504 return QPixmap::fromImage(image: img); }
6505 case QIcon::Active:
6506 return pixmap;
6507 default:
6508 break;
6509 }
6510 return pixmap;
6511}
